(103, 1, '2016-12-12 07:01:37', '2016-12-12 07:01:37', '<p><strong>newpappa</strong></p><p>December 2016</p><p>dsdsdsd. One more paragraph.</p><p>Is it possible for users to submit a support request by simply emailing a specific email, without registering and without logging in? Sort of like Craigslist?</p><p><br></p><p><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p><p><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </strong>December 2016</p><p><br></p><p>Yes, users can send an email to address configured under plugin imap settings and system will check if the sender email is registered or not, if yes, then it will create a new ticket under user’s account otherwise create a new account and create a ticket. Next time if the user reply to the agent answer, new comment will be added.</p>', 'Emailing a Specific Email', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'emailing-a-specific-email', '', '', '2018-06-20 04:37:38', '2018-06-20 04:37:38', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&#038;p=103', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(105, 1, '2016-12-12 07:03:15', '2016-12-12 07:03:15', '<b>thehotfix</b>\n\nDecember 2016\n\nHow to add “Public Tickets” and “Private Tickets” – i see no option by create a new Ticket\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>CSSJockey </b>\n\nDecember 2016\n\n&nbsp;\n\nHi, only agent or admin mark a ticket as public/private. You can set default status from plugin settings.', 'Plugin Settings', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'plugin-settings-3', '', '', '2016-12-12 07:03:15', '2016-12-12 07:03:15', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=105', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(107, 1, '2016-12-12 07:04:50', '2016-12-12 07:04:50', '<b>m2farma</b>\n\nDecember 2016\n\n&nbsp;\n\nI have a doubt you have answered before for another user, but it is not working:\n\nOther user question:\n\nWe would like to have one admin account to which all the tickets should be assigned by default – both the tickets sent by email and submitted on site. The admin can then decide to which staff the ticket has to be transferred.\n\nPlease let us know how to set this up.\n\n<b>Cheers, Jane.</b>\n\ncjrupak 18 days ago Flag Hi,\n\nTo achieve this, from our plugin settings page under Manage Staff menu:\n<ol>\n 	<li>Select the user(admin) as Support Staff (also select the user’s to which you wish to further assign the tickets) and a Fallback User.</li>\n 	<li>Then, click on Assign Departments and Products and assign All Products and All Departments to the user(admin) only.</li>\n 	<li>After the above points all Tickets will be assigned only to admin and then he needs to login into the frontend of the app and then assign the tickets to the agents he/she wishes to.</li>\n</ol>\nThanks!\n\nI tried to do what you said, the admin is set of he can see all departments, but the other users, they already have departments set for them. I can’t delete the department..', 'Plugin Settings', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'plugin-settings-4', '', '', '2016-12-12 07:04:50', '2016-12-12 07:04:50', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=107', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(109, 1, '2016-12-12 07:07:01', '2016-12-12 07:07:01', '<b>bris-emarketing</b>\n\nDecember 2016\n\n&nbsp;\n\nHi, we are planing to buy this… but I would like to ask couple of questions before we purchase.\n<ol>\n 	<li>Email enquiry can be stored automatically in the system?</li>\n 	<li>If we nominate the person (agent) who need to answer the enquiry, the person (agent) will get the notification by email?</li>\n 	<li>If the person (agent) reply the email, the system will catch the reply and send the answer email to the customer directly?</li>\n</ol>\nOur staff doesn’t want to login the system. They only wanna answer the question if they received the enquiry from the website to their email inbox.\n\nCurrently, we are using Zendesk at the moment. Do you think this application can cover what we want? Thanks!\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>CSSJockey </b>\n\nDecember 2016\n\n&nbsp;\n\nHello, Yes all this can be handled by this plugin. However, this system uses php_imap extension which process emails when the website is accessed or any page is opened in a browser. Your staff would need to reply from their dashboard within the system in the current version. However, the new version is in development and this will be covered as well with very simple setup.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>bris-emarketing</b>\n\n<b>    </b>December 2016\n\n&nbsp;\n\nThank you very much for your quick response… That means if our staff want to answer the enquiry by an email, they must be on the program has been logged in?\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>CSSJockey </b>\n\nDecember 2016\n\n&nbsp;\n\nYes, php will process all emails when the site is accessed.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>bris-emarketing</b>\n\n<b> </b>December 2016\n\nThanks for the reply. I have two more questions before we purchase.\n<ol>\n 	<li>Is there any function that the email notification will contain the direct link for the reply the enquiry? 2. Is there any option to login this system with the Google account?</li>\n</ol>\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>CSSJockey </b>\n\nDecember 2016\n\n&nbsp;\n\nEmail sent by SupportEzzy has the link to ticket and for google login you can use our Frontend Membership Modules<a href="https://goo.gl/1lM2GF."> https://goo.gl/1lM2GF.</a> I’d recommend you to try our plugins at<a href="http://cssjockey.net/"> http://cssjockey.net</a> and see if they meet all your requirements. Feel free to ask any questions once you try our products.', 'Email Enquiry', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'email-enquiry', '', '', '2016-12-12 07:07:01', '2016-12-12 07:07:01', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=109', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(111, 1, '2016-12-12 07:08:35', '2016-12-12 07:08:35', '<b>vcdesigns</b>\n\nDecember 2016\n\ni have left messages and replies to an open ticket that has been open now for a month and the information you asked for i provided twice and still nobody has done anything about this. Ticket ID: FMYQN0CC803302\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nDecember 2016\n\n&nbsp;\n\nWe really apologize for the delay and the problem has been solved and the ticket has been answered.', 'Unanswered Ticket', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'unanswered-ticket', '', '', '2016-12-12 07:08:35', '2016-12-12 07:08:35', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=111', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(114, 1, '2016-12-12 07:10:51', '2016-12-12 07:10:51', '<b>meken</b>\n\nDecember 2016\n\nmy site suddenly run into blank screen, I think it is because of email piping: Ticket ID: UEF2BM89AA3407\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nDecember 2016\n\nCan you please confirm with your host if Email Piping is enables in your server.\n\n<b>meken</b>\n\nDecember 2016\n\nSure, runs normally for 1 day, dealing with some tickets, then suddenly blank screen, from the apache error log, I think it is email-piping. Disable it via phpmyadmin, it goes ok.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>meken</b>\n\n<strong> </strong>December 2016\n\nphp7.0-imap is already the newest version (7.0.14-2+deb.sury.org~xenial+1).\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nDecember 2016\n\nAlright, we are following the issue on the ticket you had created and we will look into this further.', 'Email piping', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'email-piping-2', '', '', '2016-12-12 07:10:51', '2016-12-12 07:10:51', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=114', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(116, 1, '2016-12-12 07:13:25', '2016-12-12 07:13:25', '<b>BLUEZMEDIA</b>\n\n<b> </b>December 2016\n\n&nbsp;\n\nFor the upcoming release, does the new version/framework work as the actual ? (cf. we do not call wp_head() and wp_footer() functions on this page to avoid any layout issues, javascript conflicts and most importantly AngularJS setup.)\n\nWill it be possible to integrate it in standard wp page ? Keep the header and footer and make your plugin compatible with others !\n\nIf this the case, then please consider compatibility with Buddypress.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nDecember 2016\n\nAs long as display goes, we can still use the app with header and footer visible but the wp_footer and wp_head function are not called inside the app templates and we will try to make it more compatible with WordPress and BuddyPress too.\n\nFollow this page for more info : <a href="http://docs.cssjockey.com/cjsupport/run-app-within-a-page-with-header-and-footer/">http://docs.cssjockey.com/cjsupport/run-app-within-a-page-with-header-and-footer/</a>', 'New Version / Framework Work', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'new-version-framework-work', '', '', '2016-12-12 07:13:25', '2016-12-12 07:13:25', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=116', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(119, 1, '2016-12-12 07:15:38', '2016-12-12 07:15:38', '<b>watechno</b>\n\n<b> </b>December 2016\n\n&nbsp;\n\nI have a pre-sales question, when a client inputs his purchase code, will the system tell me if it is still a supported client or not ? because as you know, support runs out after 6 months on envato ..\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>CSSJockey</b>\n\nDecember 2016\n\n&nbsp;\n\nCurrent version is built with old api, however, new version is being developed with new api will check if support is valid or not.\n\n&nbsp;', 'Question on Purchase Code', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'question-on-purchase-code', '', '', '2016-12-12 07:15:38', '2016-12-12 07:15:38', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=119', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(121, 1, '2017-01-12 07:18:16', '2017-01-12 07:18:16', '<b>colorlink2</b>\n\nJanuary 2017\n\n&nbsp;\n\nwhen it sync woocommerce products , does it do it for each and every user request?! or does it sync by its own and shows result to ppl ?\n\nbecause over here its taking ages to open the page , after i enabled the sync .\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>`</b><b>    </b><b>colorlink2</b>\n\n<b>    </b>January 2017\n\n&nbsp;\n\nyour plugin made my server use up to 100% cpu , to sync woocommerce ,, why not just USE woocommerce products there?!\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nJanuary 2017\n\nThe woocommerce sync happens whenever admin_init hook is fired, to check if there is any new product added or not.\n\nAfter it is first initialized, i dont think you would face such a high usage moving forward.\n\nHow many products do you have?', 'Sync woocommerce', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'sync-woocommerce', '', '', '2017-01-12 07:18:16', '2017-01-12 07:18:16', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=121', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(123, 1, '2017-01-12 07:20:23', '2017-01-12 07:20:23', '<b>karll</b>\n\nJanuary 2017\n\nAny news on the new update?\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nJanuary 2017\n\nThe new version is still in development. Hopefully will be completed within this month.', 'New Update', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'new-update-3', '', '', '2017-01-12 07:20:23', '2017-01-12 07:20:23', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=123', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(125, 1, '2017-01-12 07:21:58', '2017-01-12 07:21:58', '<b>deharogroup</b>\n\nJanuary 2017\n\nThis is a pre-sale question. Is your plugin fully compatible with the Avada Theme? Just asking because I bought another plugin and the plugin wasn’t able to integrate into the My-Account section. If you would click on an order you wouldn’t see the option to report a problem with that order.\n\nAlso, does the client has the ability to submit a ticket from an existing order and the admin receive it and see which order the ticket is associated to?\n\nBasically what we need is a plugin that after the customer orders and receives the product, he can communicate with us in regard to that order if there was a problem and we can fix it for them.\n\nThanks in advance! It looks great. i just wanted to double check with you before buying it.', 'Enquiries on Plugin', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'enquiries-on-plugin', '', '', '2017-01-12 07:21:58', '2017-01-12 07:21:58', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=125', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(128, 1, '2017-01-12 07:23:42', '2017-01-12 07:23:42', '<b>BigBadBarry</b>\n\nJanuary 2017\n\n&nbsp;\n\n1: Can the the customer have multiple profiles?: i.e. one of my customers wants their manager to be able to see all support tickets their staff have raised to my company on my website\n\n2: Does this plugin send emailed when the support ticket is received / updated? if so, how customisable are these emails?\n\n3: How many customisable fields can be added to the form?\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nJanuary 2017\n\n&nbsp;\n<ol>\n 	<li>The customer cannot have multiple roles. One role per user, he can create a separate login to manage another role.</li>\n 	<li>Yes, emails are send whenever there is a new ticket or a new reply to a ticket and when a ticket is closed. Email notifications content is fully customizable.</li>\n 	<li>You can add “n” number of customisable fields to the form.</li>\n</ol>\nTo know more follow this link :<a href="http://docs.cssjockey.com/cjsupport/"> http://docs.cssjockey.com/cjsupport/</a>\n\nTo try out our plugin before purchasing follow this link : <a href="http://cssjockey.net/">http://cssjockey.net/</a>', 'Multiple Profiles', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'multiple-profiles', '', '', '2017-01-12 07:23:42', '2017-01-12 07:23:42', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=128', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(130, 1, '2017-01-12 07:25:27', '2017-01-12 07:25:27', '<b>emanuel217</b>\n\n<b> </b>January 2017\n\n&nbsp;\n\nWhy isn’t the demo site working in Internet Explorer (latest version) after logging in? Will I have the same problem if I buy the script?\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nJanuary 2017\n\n&nbsp;\n\nAre you trying it on :<a href="http://cssjockey.net/"> http://cssjockey.net/</a> ?\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>emanuel217</b>\n\n<b>    </b>January 2017\n\n&nbsp;\n\nI am trying it on:<a href="http://preview.codecanyon.net/item/supportezzy-ticket-system/full_screen_preview/8908617?_ga=1.178585124.1414904881.1483384044"> http://preview.codecanyon.net/item/supportezzy-ticket-system/full_screen_preview/8908617?_ga=1.178585124.1414904881.1483384044</a>\n\nThis is the link in the “live preview” for the plugin.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nJanuary 2017\n\nOkay, we will check this but anyways we are working on a new version of this plugin from ground up with a new technology, so we will address any issues in this new version.\n\nIt should be available by the end of next month\n\n&nbsp;', 'Demo Sight Error', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'demo-sight-error', '', '', '2017-01-12 07:25:27', '2017-01-12 07:25:27', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=130', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0) ;
