(135, 1, '2017-01-12 07:29:23', '2017-01-12 07:29:23', '<b>Soulfly999</b>\n\nJanuary 2017\n\nso it is possible to use this only with email adresses? Our user send us an email with the contact formular (formcraft) to a specific adress und then you could receive and answer the mail via Supportezzy?\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nJanuary 2017\n\nYes, this is possible with our IMAP feature. Try our plugin and IMAP feature by creating your own demo site at : <a href="http://cssjockey.net/">http://cssjockey.net/</a>\n\n&nbsp;', 'IMAP Feature', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'imap-feature', '', '', '2017-01-12 07:29:23', '2017-01-12 07:29:23', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=135', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(137, 1, '2016-10-12 07:30:51', '2016-10-12 07:30:51', '<b>sam6onzalez</b>\n\n<b> </b>October 2016\n\nPre-buy question. Are you able to create custom fields for the tickets?\n\n<b>CSSJockey</b><b>    </b>\n\nOctober 2016\n\nYes, you can. Please try the demo at <a href="http://cssjockey.net/">http://cssjockey.net</a>\n\n<b>sam6onzalez</b>\n\nOctober 2016\n\nnot reseting after submit\n\n<b>sam6onzalez</b>\n\nOctober 2016\n\nPlease ignore that… Typing in a different thread', 'Creating Custom Fields for Tickets', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'creating-custom-fields-for-work', '', '', '2016-10-12 07:30:51', '2016-10-12 07:30:51', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=137', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(141, 1, '2016-10-12 07:38:01', '2016-10-12 07:38:01', '<b>macoleco</b>\n\nOctober 2016\n\nIt has option to open a tickt without this logged in word press? But that is required insrir name and email? Wait …\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nOctober 2016\n\nNo, we cannot open a ticket without logging in.\n\n&nbsp;', 'Option to Open a New Ticket', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'option-to-open-a-new-ticket', '', '', '2016-10-12 07:38:01', '2016-10-12 07:38:01', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=141', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(144, 1, '2016-10-12 07:40:42', '2016-10-12 07:40:42', '<b>JoseDone</b>\n\nOctober 2016\n\nI want to know if the plugin support RTL or not , cause I need to use it with arabic language\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nOctober 2016\n\nSorry but our plugin does not support RTL right now.\n\n&nbsp;', 'Plugin Support RTL', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'plugin-support-rtl', '', '', '2016-10-12 07:40:42', '2016-10-12 07:40:42', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=144', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(146, 1, '2016-10-12 07:42:32', '2016-10-12 07:42:32', '<b>InvidiaMarketing</b>\n\nOctober 2016\n\nis possible to change layout with my website? I want to include ticket system into my theme and not in new layout.\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nNovember 2016\n\nYou can run the support app with a page by adding a shortcode to any page or post with Theme’s header and footer.\n\nPlease follow this link for more info : <a href="http://docs.cssjockey.com/cjsupport/run-app-within-a-page-with-header-and-footer/">http://docs.cssjockey.com/cjsupport/run-app-within-a-page-with-header-and-footer/</a>', 'Change Layout with Website', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'change-layout-with-website', '', '', '2016-10-12 07:42:32', '2016-10-12 07:42:32', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=146', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(148, 1, '2016-11-12 07:44:01', '2016-11-12 07:44:01', '<b>Bioethics</b>\n\nNovember 2016\n\nHow long is the PO file for translation? (I only have a limited number of staff, so if the PO file is too long, maybe this plugin is not for us.)', 'PO File for Translation', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'po-file-for-translation', '', '', '2016-11-12 07:44:01', '2016-11-12 07:44:01', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=148', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(151, 1, '2016-11-12 07:45:40', '2016-11-12 07:45:40', '<b>Bioethics </b>\n\n<b> </b>November 2016\n\nIs your demo system broken? I’ve created demo at<a href="http://cssjockey.net/demo/gyy3ywx0a8"> http://cssjockey.net/demo/gyy3ywx0a8</a> , but it doesn’t work.', 'Demo System Broken', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'demo-system-broken', '', '', '2016-11-12 07:45:40', '2016-11-12 07:45:40', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=151', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(153, 1, '2016-11-12 07:48:00', '2016-11-12 07:48:00', '<b>milo75</b>\n\nNovember 2016\n\nGreat job on the support system chaps. One suggestion; When you log in, instead of having a blank page maybe it can redirect you to your open tickets. Saves a click and it looks better than just a blank page.\n\n<b>milo75</b>\n\n<b> </b>November 2016\n\nAlso having the option to disable certain email notifications would be nice. Same as the auto close notification where you have the option to disable it. Can we have this for all notifications please so we can turn it on or off.\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nNovember 2016\n\nFine suggestions, we will try and include this in the upcoming version of the plugin.\n\nYou can also join us on our Facebook group to suggest any other feature (s) you wish to see in any of our product : <a href="https://facebook.com/groups/cssjockey.ib">https://facebook.com/groups/cssjockey.ib</a>', 'Disable Auto Notification', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'disable-auto-notification', '', '', '2016-11-12 07:48:00', '2016-11-12 07:48:00', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=153', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(155, 1, '2016-11-12 07:52:19', '2016-11-12 07:52:19', '<b>galaxy5</b>\n\nNovember 2016\n\nPrepurchase question: With email piping can we use our own custom SMTP like mailgun instead of our the server, I don’t want our original IP address leaking out.\n\n<b>CSSJockey</b>\n\n<b> </b>November 2016\n\nthe current version uses only php imap for email piping. However, we will consider adding more services in our upcoming version.', 'Email Piping', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'email-piping-3', '', '', '2016-11-12 07:52:19', '2016-11-12 07:52:19', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=155', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
