(245, 1, '2016-08-14 04:53:04', '2016-08-14 04:53:04', '<b>m2farma</b>\n\nAugust 2016\n\nI want everybody here to know that the support after you buy is really really slow in solving the problems. Open your ticket and take a site because it will take weeks! I’m really desapointed.', 'Slow Support', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'slow-support', '', '', '2016-08-14 04:53:04', '2016-08-14 04:53:04', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=245', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(247, 1, '2016-08-14 04:58:07', '2016-08-14 04:58:07', '<b>szed</b>\n\nAugust 2016\n\nAnyone with a french translation ?\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nAugust 2016\n\nSorry, we don’t have anyone for French Translation.', 'French Translation', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'french-translation', '', '', '2016-08-14 04:58:07', '2016-08-14 04:58:07', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=247', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(249, 1, '2016-08-14 05:00:18', '2016-08-14 05:00:18', '<b>BoRo85</b>\n\nAugust 2016\n\nI have a pre-sale question:\n\nDoes your Plugin work with Buddypress?\n\nOn my Site I use the “Thrive Intranet &amp; Community WordPress Theme” with WP-CRM &amp; WP-Invoice, document management, etc. Is it compatible?\n\nI need a general overview of all interactions with the customer\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nAugust 2016\n\nThis plugin does not work with other plugins and other plugin’s shortcodes also does not work and here is reason why :<a href="http://docs.cssjockey.com/cjsupport/why-other-shortcodes-and-plugins-dont-work-on-this-page/"> http://docs.cssjockey.com/cjsupport/why-other-shortcodes-and-plugins-dont-work-on-this-page/</a>\n\nHowever, the user’s registered by BuddyPress can be used in the app.\n\nHere is the list of all the features of this plugin : http://docs.cssjockey.com/cjsupport/\n\n&nbsp;', 'Plugin with Buddypress', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'plugin-with-buddypress', '', '', '2016-08-14 05:00:18', '2016-08-14 05:00:18', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=249', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(251, 1, '2016-08-14 05:03:18', '2016-08-14 05:03:18', '<strong>OdiGames</strong>\n\nAugust 2016\n\nI tried to read the docs at <a href="http://docs.cssjockey.com/cjsupport/" rel="nofollow">http://docs.cssjockey.com/cjsupport/</a> but your site is down… get this message: Error establishing a database connection\n\nSame for the demo website.\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/cjrupak">cjrupak</a></strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">August 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">All that have been fixed now.</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response"></div>', 'Error Establishing a Database Connection', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'error-establishing-a-database-connection', '', '', '2016-08-14 05:03:18', '2016-08-14 05:03:18', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=251', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(254, 1, '2016-08-14 05:11:21', '2016-08-14 05:11:21', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>thesoftwarepeople</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">August 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI really would like a refund for my purchase. I just tried to leave a support ticket on your website and the error message says “Error Establishing Database Connection”. That error message has been the theme of my usage of the plugin. It was totally unusable and I would like my credits. I know more than 24hrs have passed but there was no way I could continue to use this without sacrificing using other plugins on the site. Issues included:\n\n- Plugin would prevent other plugins from sending email (ie Contact Form 7, sends notification email but wont send autoresponder email with your plugin active) - Users could not scroll ticket comments - Your plugin activation caused some plugin features on left admin menu to disappear.\n\nAnd given a refund, you wont have to worry about me still using the plugin, I cant use it now. Thanks\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_14114912" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><strong>cjrupak</strong></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">August 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">Can you please raise a refund request from your Envato Dashboard.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Error Establishing Database Connection', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'error-establishing-database-connection', '', '', '2016-08-14 05:11:21', '2016-08-14 05:11:21', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=254', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(256, 1, '2016-08-14 05:16:12', '2016-08-14 05:16:12', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>zibaloon2 </strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">August 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello I updated .po file and I can see my translation when I was login, But when I logout can not see my translation and see original words.\n\n<strong>Cjrupak</strong>\n\nAugust 2016\n\nCan you please create a ticket at <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com/</a> so that we can get site details and help you debug the issue.\n\n</div>\n</div>', 'Translation Error', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'translation-error', '', '', '2016-08-14 05:16:12', '2016-08-14 05:16:12', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=256', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
