(353, 1, '2016-06-14 11:13:29', '2016-06-14 11:13:29', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/genloc">genloc</a> </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">June 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, are problems with WordPress 4.5 known? Runs the ticket system with the new WordPress version?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13119646" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/cjrupak">cjrupak</a> </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">June 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">We have yet to test the complete plugin on WordPress 4.5. We will publish an update if required and will update the info on Codecanyon that it is fully compatible with 4.5</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Problems with Wordpress 4.5', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'problems-with-wordpress-4-5', '', '', '2016-06-14 11:13:29', '2016-06-14 11:13:29', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=353', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(355, 1, '2016-06-14 11:15:44', '2016-06-14 11:15:44', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/eddieneg">eddieneg</a></strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">June 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, after updating to new wordpress version , now the respond / answer option of the ticket is disables. Now I can’t answer or reply withing the ticket on the front end.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13119672" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/cjrupak">cjrupak</a> </strong></p>\nJune 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n&nbsp;\n\nWe are testing our plugin features on WordPress 4.5. We will look into this problem and can you also please create a ticket for this issue on <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com/</a> so that we can keep a track of the issue and keep you updated on the same.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13167546" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/eddieneg">eddieneg</a></strong></div>\n<div class="media__item">June 2016</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, have you solved the problem ??\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13173290" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/cjrupak">cjrupak</a> </strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">June 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nWhile testing on 4.5 we have not faced this problem and we were able to respond and answer the ticket. There can be some other reasons that it is not working for you.\n\nOnce we get the info to your website, we will look into it.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Respond Option is Disable', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'respond-option-is-disable', '', '', '2016-06-14 11:15:44', '2016-06-14 11:15:44', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=355', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(358, 1, '2016-06-14 11:21:06', '2016-06-14 11:21:06', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30"><p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cfu3i29</strong></p></div><div class="media__body -align-center"><div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">June 2016</div></div><div class="comment__body"><div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">Any ETA on the new version and any list of planned new features available? - Will it possible to deactivate the creation of new accounts when new tickets are created from emails, i.e. to have them as “guest” tickets?</div></div><div class="js-comment comment__item-response"><div id="comment_13134121" class="comment__info"><div class="media"><div class="media__item">&nbsp;<br></div><div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30"><p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cfu3i29</strong></p></div><div class="media__body -align-center"><div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">June 2016</div><div>&nbsp;<br></div></div></div></div><div class="comment__body--response"><div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted"><br></div></div><div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container">&nbsp;<br></div></div><div class="js-comment comment__item-response"><div id="comment_13141111" class="comment__info"><div class="media"><div class="media__item">&nbsp;<br></div><div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30"><p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/cjrupak">cjrupak</a></strong></p>June 2016</div></div></div><div class="comment__body--response"><div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">The new version would still take at least another month. Probably in this month or by the end of next. List of new features will be rolled out after the development of the new version is completed, as we got many updates and new features and we will see which ones are most important and which ones can be released later under minor updates on a regular basis. But the features you have listed above will definitely be included in the upcoming version of the plugin.</div></div></div><div class="js-comment comment__item-response"><div id="comment_13568321" class="comment__info"><div class="media"><div class="media__item">&nbsp;<br></div><div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30"><p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/cfu3i29">cfu3i29</a></strong></p></div><div class="media__body -align-center"><div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">June 2016</div><div>&nbsp;<br></div></div></div></div><div class="comment__body--response"><div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">Do you also have any plans to make it possible for users to access tickets created by email from different email addresses (i.e. separate user accounts for support users which allow multiple email addresses)? Reason: people often have more than one email address and don’t necessarily always use the one attached to their WP account.</div></div><div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container">&nbsp;<br></div></div><div class="js-comment comment__item-response"><div id="comment_13592889" class="comment__info"><div class="media"><div class="media__item">&nbsp;<br></div><div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30"><p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/cjrupak">cjrupak</a></strong></p></div><div class="media__body -align-center"><div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">June 2016</div><div>&nbsp;<br></div></div></div></div><div class="comment__body--response"><div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">No plans to include this feature yet but we like the idea and we will try and make this possible down the road, as we proceed to elaborate this plugin and make it more and more flexible and customizable.</div></div></div>', 'ETA on the New Version', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'eta-on-the-new-version', '', '', '2018-04-16 11:18:06', '2018-04-16 11:18:06', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&#038;p=358', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(360, 1, '2016-06-14 11:26:45', '2016-06-14 11:26:45', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30"><p><br></p><p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/timesoftimes">timesoftimes</a></strong></p></div><div class="media__body -align-center"><div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">June 2016</div><div><br></div></div><div class="comment__body"><div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted"><p>can convert as a mobile app?</p></div></div><div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden">ewewew ew</div><div class="js-comment comment__item-response"><div id="comment_13186594" class="comment__info"><div class="media"><div class="media__item"><br></div><div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30"><p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p><p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">June 2016</p><p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">Not as an app as of now but it would work on all resolutions as it is responsive.</p></div></div></div></div>', 'Convert as a Mobile App', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'convert-as-a-mobile-app', '', '', '2018-06-20 04:38:14', '2018-06-20 04:38:14', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&#038;p=360', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(362, 1, '2016-06-14 11:28:44', '2016-06-14 11:28:44', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>afflabs</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">June 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nUsername / password for Technical Support Agent are still not working. Where can we test admin panel or get updated login info?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13251887" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/cjrupak">cjrupak</a></strong></p>\nJune 216\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nWe are fixing the issue and by the time you can create your own demo site at : <a href="http://cssjockey.net/" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net/</a> and in there you can activate all our products/plugins and also add any other plugin or theme and check that with our products.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Technical Support Agent', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'technical-support-agent', '', '', '2016-06-14 11:28:44', '2016-06-14 11:28:44', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=362', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0) ;
