(366, 1, '2016-06-14 11:41:58', '2016-06-14 11:41:58', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>sandron</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">June 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nWhen trying to create ticket or viewing tickets, the right pane is blank for a logged in user.\n\nPractically the plugin is unusable for me. Created a ticket 20 hours ago. Didn’t get a response yet.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13291174" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">June 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nOur support timings are from Monday to Friday ( 10AM to 6PM IST ).\n\nAlso, I can see that your support has been expired but still we have replied to your ticket today itself. Please check.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'The Right Pane is Blank', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'the-right-pane-is-blank', '', '', '2016-06-14 11:41:58', '2016-06-14 11:41:58', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=366', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(368, 1, '2016-06-15 04:59:21', '2016-06-15 04:59:21', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>bagonline</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">June 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nIs there frontend registration / login for the user? I don’t want users going to wp-admin (wordpress backend).\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12398892" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><strong>CSSJockey</strong> <span class="e-text-label -color-grey -size-s">  </span></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">June 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nYes this can be done, try this plugin at <a href="http://cssjockey.net/" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Frontend Registration', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'frontend-registration', '', '', '2016-06-15 04:59:21', '2016-06-15 04:59:21', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=368', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(370, 1, '2016-06-15 05:03:27', '2016-06-15 05:03:27', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>dtommy79</strong></p>\nJune 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nAny chance for adding support for easy digital downloads?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12398533" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">June 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">Right now we are more focused on upgrading the plugin. Removing any bugs and making it more stable.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nMaybe down the line, we might try and make it compatible with other major plugins out there like Easy Digital Downloads.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Adding Easy Digital Downloads', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'adding-easy-digital-downloads', '', '', '2016-06-15 05:03:27', '2016-06-15 05:03:27', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=370', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(372, 1, '2016-06-15 05:12:08', '2016-06-15 05:12:08', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>jeffgipson</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">June 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI need help I submitted a ticket but no response yet… I setup up the plugin but I don’t see my logo or any content on the support page except placeholders any help on this ?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12398455" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">June 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">Can you please mention the Ticket ID, so that we can take a look.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'No Response', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'no-response', '', '', '2016-06-15 05:12:08', '2016-06-15 05:12:08', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=372', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(374, 1, '2016-06-15 05:14:00', '2016-06-15 05:14:00', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>ericho09</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">June 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nemail pipe issue, when I use <a href="mailto:xxx@yahoo.com">xxx@yahoo.com</a>, it is 100% NOT create ticket. I tried two yahoo.com emails and both not working with no email received back from email pipe.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12420201" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">June 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nYou query has been answered on the ticket created.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12440134" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>ericho09</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">June 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted"><a href="mailto:helpdesk@cssjockey.com">helpdesk@cssjockey.com</a> doesn’t work for any of my yahoo emails too. Please help to check.</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Email Pipe Issue', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'email-pipe-issue', '', '', '2016-06-15 05:14:00', '2016-06-15 05:14:00', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=374', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(378, 1, '2016-06-15 05:30:39', '2016-06-15 05:30:39', '&nbsp;\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>jacklee2</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">June 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi there , Can i know this plugin allow Admin to manage the ticket ?? Example Admin can be see the report for support agent conversation with client and how the performance with the staff ?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12455865" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>jacklee2</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">June 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nAnd can i know the ticket able to be private ?? mean only the client and support agent able to see .\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12466071" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">June 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n1. The Admin would be able to manage tickets. He can also create a new ticket from the WordPress dashboard even. We right now do not have an extensive reporting section in this plugin but the admin can check the tickets and the comments on it in the backend and judge the performance.\n\n2. Yes, the tickets are totally private and only the agent to whom the product has been assigned will be able to see the tickets related to that product &amp; client will only be able to see his ticket unless marked as public.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Managing the Plugin', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'managing-the-plugin', '', '', '2016-06-15 05:30:39', '2016-06-15 05:30:39', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=378', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(381, 1, '2016-06-15 05:33:44', '2016-06-15 05:33:44', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>jerweb </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">June 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nJust wondering if there is Any ETA on new version have a project which still cannot go online and really waiting on update\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12466078" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">June 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">You can expect the new version of this plugin in 2 months time. Somewhere around the end of April.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'ETA Update', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'eta-update', '', '', '2016-06-15 05:33:44', '2016-06-15 05:33:44', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=381', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(383, 1, '2016-06-15 05:35:43', '2016-06-15 05:35:43', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>marianstancu</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">June 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello! Very nice plugin, congratulations! But! So slow!!!! Something is not right, I think. I try this on two powerful servers, but still slow… Is it possible to do something about that?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12488797" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">June 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n&nbsp;\n\nHave you tried deactivating other plugins or test it on a default WordPress theme.\n\nIt can be a conflict issue while loading plugin resources.\n\nYou can also try some cache plugin(s) to speed up the process.\n\nIf none works, please open a ticket on our support portal at <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com/</a> and we will look into it.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Slow Process', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'slow-process', '', '', '2016-06-15 05:35:43', '2016-06-15 05:35:43', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=383', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(385, 1, '2016-04-15 05:38:02', '2016-04-15 05:38:02', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>eduardocs </strong></p>\nApril 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nWhen I open a ticket I do not receive my email notification…HELP!!!\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12488814" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\nApril 2016\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nIt can be a problem with the server or with mail SMTP settings. Can you please first take a look at the mail error logs on your server.\n\nIf everything seems fine, please open a ticket on our support portal at <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com/</a> and we will help you debug the issue.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Server Problem', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'server-problem', '', '', '2016-04-15 05:38:02', '2016-04-15 05:38:02', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=385', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(387, 1, '2016-04-15 05:43:54', '2016-04-15 05:43:54', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>thesoftwarepeople</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">Aoril 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nYour demo page isn’t working…it says error establishing database connection.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12583121" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">April 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThank you for notification, sorted the issue.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Demo Page Error', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'demo-page-error', '', '', '2016-04-15 05:43:54', '2016-04-15 05:43:54', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=387', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(389, 1, '2016-04-15 05:48:33', '2016-04-15 05:48:33', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>sanket2612</strong></p>\nApril 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nYour site is showing Error establishing database connection. Not even able to verify the plugin by entering the purchase code pls fix it ASAP…\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12559540" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">April 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">Sorry for the inconvenience.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nIt has been fixed now.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Error Establishing Database Connection', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'error-establishing-database-connection-2', '', '', '2016-04-15 05:48:33', '2016-04-15 05:48:33', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=389', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(391, 1, '2016-04-15 05:53:36', '2016-04-15 05:53:36', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>thesoftwarepeople</strong></p>\nApril 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI keep re-entering my purchase code and it will not acknowledge that its entered nor show any messages about its status.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12559571" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">April 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">Our site was facing some technical issues. We have fixed it now, please try again and if you still face an issue, you can open a ticket on our support portal at : <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com/</a></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Re-Entering the Purchase Code', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 're-entering-the-purchase-code', '', '', '2016-04-15 05:53:36', '2016-04-15 05:53:36', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=391', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(393, 1, '2016-04-15 05:57:59', '2016-04-15 05:57:59', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>bmxtraining</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">April 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nCan users add youtube video code in their support ticket?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12607902" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">June 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">The video embed code will not work in the support ticket.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nIt will not be converted to a video and the code itself would get displayed.\n\nThe links for the video would work and for the links, you can choose whether to open the link in the same window or a new window. This can be done by clicking on the link icon on the top of ticket editor.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12607942" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">April 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nOne more thing, if someone has posted a video embed link in the ticket the video will be displayed in the email response he would get.\n\nThis work in Gmail, not sure about other email providers.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12624637" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>bmxtraining</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">April 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nCould this be changed? I would like clients to paste a youtube link and have the video show in the ticket text body like native wordpress does it\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12629151" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">April 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nWe will be enhancing the Editor in our next release and our next version will be out probably in 2 months time.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Adding Youtube Video code', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'adding-youtube-video-code', '', '', '2016-04-15 05:57:59', '2016-04-15 05:57:59', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=393', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(395, 1, '2016-04-15 06:02:18', '2016-04-15 06:02:18', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>janxcode</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">April 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, I have purchased the plugin, now i need to make clients register with envato item purchase code. How i can achieve that?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12644853" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">April 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">We cannot register clients with Envato Purchase code, however if you enable Envato Marketplace Integration from the plugin settings, after the ticket submission plugin would let you know if the client is a verified customer or not.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Register with Envato', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'register-with-envato', '', '', '2016-04-15 06:02:18', '2016-04-15 06:02:18', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=395', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(397, 1, '2016-03-15 06:11:02', '2016-03-15 06:11:02', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>HeeHA</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"> March 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI would like to use a member plugin for our members.\n\nUser Profiles Made Easy plugin <a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/user-profiles-made-easy-wordpress-plugin/4109874">http://codecanyon.net/item/user-profiles-made-easy-wordpress-plugin/4109874</a>Is it integrate the member system?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12644920" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">March 2016</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n&nbsp;\n\nWe haven’t tested our plugin with User Profiles Made Easy but I don’t think it would be a problem to use any plugin that helps you create user profiles.\n\nAs our plugin uses the default WordPress user’s base and it doesn’t matter from where or which platform the user has registered to login into the support portal as long as the user is registered in WordPress user’s table.\n\nStill if you have doubts you can test our plugin and the User Profile Made Easy plugin together on <a href="http://cssjockey.net/" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net/</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Member Plugin', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'member-plugin', '', '', '2016-03-15 06:11:02', '2016-03-15 06:11:02', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=397', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(401, 1, '2016-03-15 06:30:56', '2016-03-15 06:30:56', '&nbsp;\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>thrempel</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">March 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nPre sale questions:\n\nI have tested the demo site, and i can’t upload files (even if they are smaller than 5mb), any bug or is just with the demo?\n\nCan i upgrade the files maximum size?\n\nCan i change, or create custom fields for the new ticket area?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12655735" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">March 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">1. It must be the demo site only, you can try the file upload on our live support portal by creating a demo ticket at <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com/</a></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n2. The maximum size depends on the maximum size specified for the WordPress. So it would be equal to whatever upload size has been set for the WordPress installation and you can change the text 5MB to anything.\n\n3. We cannot change the default fields on creating new ticket area but we can add custom fields to it.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Upgrade the Files', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'upgrade-the-files', '', '', '2016-03-15 06:30:56', '2016-03-15 06:30:56', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=401', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(404, 1, '2016-03-15 06:46:19', '2016-03-15 06:46:19', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>fidraman</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">March 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello Is this plugin RTL ready ? and can I add a map field in the ticket form ? so the admin can know exactly where is the problem in the map. Thank you\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12655854" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">March 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">RTL is not supported in this version but we will try and add RTL support in our next update.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nAre we talking about Google Maps? I am not able to get exactly what this map field would do? as we certainly can add custom fields to the new ticket form. Can you elaborate more on this map field?\n\nYou can also test our plugin at <a href="http://cssjockey.net/" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net/</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12657660" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>fidraman</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">March 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThank you for the quick replay. 1 – I hope the RTL support will come out as soon as possible so I can purchase it and use as my official support ticket. 2 – about the map field, yes it’s about google maps, the user can put the location pin anywhere in the map, and when apply the form, I, as an admin, I can see the same location in google map in the form along with other information .. 3- the user interface is it in the frond end of the WordPress setup (can it be in a page or a post ?) or in the back-end ? 4 – one more thing please, Is the user have to sign up in the website in order to submit a ticket ? Thank you a bunch.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12677358" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">March 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">The map feature is not available in right now but I think this is a good feature to add. We will consider it and try our best to include this in our next update but no promises though as adding a feature like this takes a lot’s of consideration and time to incorporate.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nYes, the user has to sign-in in order to submit a ticket as this app was created keeping in mind to give support to premium customers/clients and not to make it as a public forum.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Plugin RTL', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'plugin-rtl', '', '', '2016-03-15 06:46:19', '2016-03-15 06:46:19', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=404', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(406, 1, '2016-03-15 06:49:29', '2016-03-15 06:49:29', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>exisadmin</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">March 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello, Is it possible to have different client groups (e.g. moms and dads) that can views different categories to address their tickets?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12677392" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">March 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">The tickets can be grouped only by the following:</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n1. Status (Open, Close, Awaiting Response &amp; Public) 2. Departments. 3. Products.\n\nOther than those I am afraid we cannot have any other group or groups to categorize the tickets.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Different Client Groups', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'different-client-groups', '', '', '2016-03-15 06:49:29', '2016-03-15 06:49:29', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=406', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(408, 1, '2016-03-15 06:51:18', '2016-03-15 06:51:18', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>TheChrisLusk</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">March 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThe ONLY thing lacking is a robust reporting tool. From the admin area is there a way to export all the tickets to a CSV file? I want to see how many tickets have been opened in each category or product by which clients, etc.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12712565" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">March 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">We already have a good Reporting Tool for the admin area in our development pipeline.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nRight now we cannot export tickets to a CSV file but for, now maybe you can use some other plugin that imports post data with comments, categories, etc… in a CSV file, as tickets are created as a custom post type with the name Tickets and the comments on the ticket are saved as WordPress Comments of that particular post(ticket).\n\nWe will give this feature in our next update.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12981540" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>TheChrisLusk</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">March 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThanks for the heads up. We are willing to pay for this as a separate plugin because we need it so badly.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Robust Reporting Tool', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'robust-reporting-tool', '', '', '2016-03-15 06:51:18', '2016-03-15 06:51:18', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=408', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(410, 1, '2016-03-15 06:54:14', '2016-03-15 06:54:14', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>eddieneg</strong></p>\nMarch 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, I just wanted to seknow if the Ticket could be exported as a pdf so it can also be used as a tangible paper ticket?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12712636" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/cjrupak">c</a>jrupak</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">March 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">Unfortunately, in this version we cannot export a ticket to PDF.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Ticket Export as PDF', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'ticket-export-as-pdf', '', '', '2016-03-15 06:54:14', '2016-03-15 06:54:14', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=410', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(412, 1, '2016-02-15 06:57:40', '2016-02-15 06:57:40', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>jerweb</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nany news about update?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12033023" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nFebruary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHey, we are working on it. there’s a lot to do and we are trying our best to complete and test this new version asap.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Updates', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'updates-3', '', '', '2016-02-15 06:57:40', '2016-02-15 06:57:40', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=412', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(414, 1, '2016-02-15 07:09:00', '2016-02-15 07:09:00', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>wprangers</strong></p>\nFebruary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\ncongratulations CSSJockey for making such a useful plugin, i was planing to start my support system with ticksy.com but after looking at your plugin i have decided to go for my self hosted solution.\n\ni have gone through all previous comments and i can understand that you a have a long list of items for the new version.\n\ni need a support system with-in a month as i am planning to release my first theme on themeforest. can you please give an idea as by when you can release the latest version? so that i can plan my schedule.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219391" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, Sorry for the delay in reply. Its taking a little longer than expected as the list is pretty huge, I think it is going to take another month or so.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Useful Plugin', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'useful-plugin', '', '', '2016-02-15 07:09:00', '2016-02-15 07:09:00', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=414', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(416, 1, '2016-02-15 07:12:46', '2016-02-15 07:12:46', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>xbhj308dh</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">February 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello, works with the new WP version?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219361" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">February 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nYes, it does.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'New WP Version', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'new-wp-version', '', '', '2016-02-15 07:12:46', '2016-02-15 07:12:46', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=416', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(418, 1, '2016-02-15 07:18:53', '2016-02-15 07:18:53', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>phatmano </strong></p>\nFebruary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI see you are also the author of Paid Content Packages Subscriptions. How does SupportEzzy Ticket System work with Paid Content Packages Subscriptions? Do they integrate at all? The solution I am looking for is a paid subscription support system. The scenario is simple: users buy monthly subscriptions and gain access to a level of support according to membership they paid for.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219347" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, Yes we do have Paid Content Packages in our portfolio however, they are not linked with each other as of now. We are in process of re-creating our plugins from scratch which will have these features included.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Paid Content Packages Subscriptions', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'paid-content-packages-subscriptions', '', '', '2016-02-15 07:18:53', '2016-02-15 07:18:53', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=418', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(420, 1, '2016-02-15 07:21:19', '2016-02-15 07:21:19', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>phatmano</strong></p>\nFebruary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nWhere’s the demo for sign up pricing tables? And are there different presets?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219327" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">February 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, paid tickets and pricing tables are not included with this plugin.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Demo for Signing Up', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'demo-for-signing-up', '', '', '2016-02-15 07:21:19', '2016-02-15 07:21:19', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=420', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(422, 1, '2016-02-15 07:24:00', '2016-02-15 07:24:00', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>simplyd</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">February 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\ntrying to setup email piping… but getting the error:\n\nCould not connect to IMAP server, please check and try again.\n\nCan’t connect to xxxxxxxxx,993: Connection timed out\n\ni tried with and without tls port 143/993\n\nalso tried with mailserver hostname and ip address\n\nnothing works, i can login to the mail account seperately with the credentials i am putting in\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12159460" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>simplyd</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">February 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\ni purchased this 4 days ago, and have requested support but nothing… surely you should not be selling a product on here if you cannot support it?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219290" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHey, sorry for the delay in replies here. Please create a ticket at <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com</a> with temp admin account and email details.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Email Piping', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'email-piping-4', '', '', '2016-02-15 07:24:00', '2016-02-15 07:24:00', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=422', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(425, 1, '2016-02-15 07:27:07', '2016-02-15 07:27:07', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>Jawad96</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">February 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi there,\n\nThis appears to be a comprehensive support plugin. I have a pre sale question – I intend to use this alongside WooCommerce.\n\nIt says I am able to set this up on a new Wordpress installation. Preferably I would like to add it to a sub-domain of support.mysite.com and have it linked to my main site so when customers click on support if they are logged in already on my main site then they will also be logged in on the support site. Not only this but it should also be able to check for WooCommerce order history etc\n\nIs this possible?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219317" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, the login functions will work if it is a multisite install. However, Woocommerce needs to the on same site.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Woocommerce', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'woocommerce-3', '', '', '2016-02-15 07:27:07', '2016-02-15 07:27:07', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=425', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0) ;
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` ( `ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES
(427, 1, '2016-02-15 07:29:40', '2016-02-15 07:29:40', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>BigStache</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">February 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nAfter logging into the demo site as a client it appears that I can see all tickets. Even from other clients? Is that correct? I would not want one client to see other clients tickets.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219309" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, I’d recommend you to test this plugin at <a href="http://cssjockey.net/" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net</a> as an admin. Create different accounts for agents and clients and setup the plugin the way you want to check if it meets your requirements.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Plugin Test', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'plugin-test', '', '', '2016-02-15 07:29:40', '2016-02-15 07:29:40', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=427', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(429, 1, '2016-02-15 07:32:02', '2016-02-15 07:32:02', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>TheChrisLusk</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThis is probably one of the best plugins, BY FAR, on Envato! Really great job guys.\n\nFEEDBACK: Give labels and input groups classes or ID’s so they can be hidden easier (such as the URL box and priority) with CSS, or give an option to hide these since they are not required.\n\nQUESTION: How can I include my custom fields in the email messages?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219300" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/CSSJockey">CSSJockey</a> </strong></p>\nFebruary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThank you for your feedback, we will sort this in upcoming versions. Currently it is not possible to include the user input into email messages, however, we will include this option as well.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12236133" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>TheChrisLusk</strong></p>\nFebruary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nCool, any idea when this will be available? Pretty important to know the custom fields which is why we added them <img title=":)" src="https://codecanyon.net/images/smileys/happy.png" alt=":)" />\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12287624" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nWe are working hard to roll out the new version as soon as possible, however the list of features is pretty long and it will take us at least another month to roll out the new version.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13367631" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>TheChrisLusk</strong></p>\nFebruary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nChecking to see if the latest update had the possibility to include the custom fields in the notification emails? It seems useless to create a custom field and then not be able to send that data in the ticket email….right?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Best Plugins', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'best-plugins', '', '', '2016-02-15 07:32:02', '2016-02-15 07:32:02', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=429', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(431, 1, '2016-02-15 07:39:43', '2016-02-15 07:39:43', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>Harlock_</strong></p>\nFebruary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, I need to offer ticket support for a woocommerce product but I need it to end after a determined period (i.e. a week). Is it possible? Thanks, Francesco\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219285" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, it is not possible as the system doesn’t trigger any such action. You need to keep track of time.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Ticket Support', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'ticket-support', '', '', '2016-02-15 07:39:43', '2016-02-15 07:39:43', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=431', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(433, 1, '2016-03-15 07:41:50', '2016-03-15 07:41:50', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>wellsb</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">March 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nQuestion: If I assign a ticket to a group can I also assign it to an individual as well. For example: Ticket comes in – I assign it to System Group and I need to assign it my manager Jane Doe.\n\nIf so, how?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219275" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">March 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, in current version assigning to an individual is not possible.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Assigning Tickets', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'assigning-tickets-2', '', '', '2016-03-15 07:41:50', '2016-03-15 07:41:50', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=433', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(435, 1, '2016-01-15 07:44:11', '2016-01-15 07:44:11', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>wellsb</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI can seem to log into support ez using the admin login\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219271" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">January 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nUsers with admin account can login to the support portal.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Admin Account', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'admin-account-2', '', '', '2016-01-15 07:44:11', '2016-01-15 07:44:11', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=435', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(437, 1, '2016-05-15 07:46:29', '2016-05-15 07:46:29', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>QualityMead </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">May 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nCan only registered users do email piping?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219268" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">May 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nNope, new user will be created if the email is not registered in the system.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Email Piping', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'email-piping-5', '', '', '2016-05-15 07:46:29', '2016-05-15 07:46:29', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=437', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(440, 1, '2016-02-16 14:43:32', '2016-02-16 14:43:32', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/iqit-commerce">iqit-commerce</a></strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">February 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThere is 500 internal error when i try do create test demo after receiving link on mail\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12264516" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>iqit-commerce</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">February 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nbtw I saw you working on new update, do you have any timeline? becouse if it will be near future i will probably wait for new update with mu support system change\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12287608" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nFebruary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, I’ll check the demo site and fix any issues this week. New version will take some time as the list of features we are adding is pretty long and it will take time to fully implement all these features and test everything before we rollout the new version.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Internal Error', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'internal-error', '', '', '2016-02-16 14:43:32', '2016-02-16 14:43:32', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=440', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(442, 1, '2016-02-16 15:02:18', '2016-02-16 15:02:18', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>abokamel</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, iam interesting to purchase this plugin but i have some queries: RTL well supported or no? user can reply via email or no? in email notification could i put the sender email anything like <a href="mailto:support@mywebsite.com">support@mywebsite.com</a> ? thanks\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12287596" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, RTL is not fully tested, however, you can test this plugin and all its features at <a href="http://cssjockey.net./" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net.</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'RTL Support', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'rtl-support', '', '', '2016-02-16 15:02:18', '2016-02-16 15:02:18', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=442', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(444, 1, '2016-02-16 15:07:45', '2016-02-16 15:07:45', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>brianoneill</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">February 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI am looking at the demo. When I click on SCR nothing happens? I am looking a ticket and knowledge base system, can you product do public SCR? If yes can you give me a link to a working demo?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12399079" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nFebruary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi,\n\nHave you tried it on <a href="http://cssjockey.net/?" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net?</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Knowledge Base System', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'knowledge-base-system', '', '', '2016-02-16 15:07:45', '2016-02-16 15:07:45', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=444', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(446, 1, '2016-01-16 15:13:33', '2016-01-16 15:13:33', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CrossLeaf</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nJanuary 2016\n\nWhat CSS script would I have to add to change the Green Buttons? In particular the most visible ones “Create New Ticket” “Transfer Ticket” “Post Response”\n\nThank you very much.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12399012" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThe class to change the green buttons is ’.btn-success’.\n\nJust add the following to our Custom CSS/Javascript page in the plugin settings:\n<h1>supportezzy .btn-success</h1>\n{ background-color: #your_color_code; border-color: #color_code_matching_the_bg_color; }\n\nCaution: It would change all the green buttons in the app.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Create New Ticket', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'create-new-ticket', '', '', '2016-01-16 15:13:33', '2016-01-16 15:13:33', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=446', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(448, 1, '2016-01-16 15:16:12', '2016-01-16 15:16:12', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>stefan872 </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHow can i delete the unique code in the subject of the emails like this one: [SIW5WYI4BA102]\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12398934" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThis cannot be removed as it is needed to track tickets with IMAP.\n\nOtherwise, the comments on a ticket would be treated as a new and separate ticket.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Deleting Unique Code', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'deleting-unique-code', '', '', '2016-01-16 15:16:12', '2016-01-16 15:16:12', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=448', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(450, 1, '2016-01-16 15:21:46', '2016-01-16 15:21:46', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>franwess</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n&nbsp;\n\nJanuary 2016\n\nI have a pre-sales question related to a comment from a use above which I quote here:\n\n<em>“Question: If I assign a ticket to a group can I also assign it to an individual as well. For example: Ticket comes in – I assign it to System Group and I need to assign it my manager Jane Doe. If so, how?</em>\n<em>Hi, in current version assigning to an individual is not possible.”</em>\n\nDoes this mean that I can not assign tickets to individuals within a group or does it only mean that when assigned to a group, I cannot also assign to an individual? In other words, what I’m asking is whether tickets are assigned to individuals within groups or only to the group itself?\n\nIf I cannot assign to an individual, how are support agents held accountable?\n\nKind regards Francois Wessels\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12399343" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nIt is assigned to the individual inside a group (department).\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Assigning a Ticket', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'assigning-a-ticket', '', '', '2016-01-16 15:21:46', '2016-01-16 15:21:46', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=450', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(452, 1, '2016-01-16 15:33:27', '2016-01-16 15:33:27', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>radioative</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi. My client can send an email to create a ticket or must login into the system do create one?\n\nI’d like to use this for customer support.\n\n1) My client send an email. (<a href="mailto:support@example.com">support@example.com</a>) 2) System converts this email to a ticket 3) I’ll use this system to respond and manage tickets. 4) When I respond, my client receive the response in email.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12399416" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nAny email sent to the set email address in the plugin settings under IMAP Configuration will be a new ticket and any replies to that email will be converted to comments.\n\nYou can try the plugin on <a href="http://cssjokcey.net/" rel="nofollow">http://cssjokcey.net</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Respond and Manage Tickets', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'respond-and-manage-tickets', '', '', '2016-01-16 15:33:27', '2016-01-16 15:33:27', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=452', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(456, 1, '2016-01-19 03:46:23', '2016-01-19 03:46:23', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>sanderdatema</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI set one department and one product (because I don’t need them), but when you want to assign a ticket to another agent, the form still wants me to choose a department and product.\n\n1. Why ask if there’s no choice when there’s only on option? 2. Can it be turned off?\n\nThanks.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11722290" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThank you for your feedback, will sort this in upcoming version.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Assigning a Ticket', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'assigning-a-ticket-2', '', '', '2016-01-19 03:46:23', '2016-01-19 03:46:23', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=456', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(458, 1, '2016-01-19 03:49:27', '2016-01-19 03:49:27', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>extensionforge </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\none of the best solutions for support/helpdesk I saw in the last years and thats one of the reasons to move from zendesk into my homepage.\n\nOne thing I’m wondering is – Is it possible to show the F.A.Q. inside the ticket system layout and not making a switch to the normal page-theme? Maybe I have tomatoes on my eyes : )\n\nAnd some featurewishes:\n- Statistics View\n- Option to add menue items\n- Frontend login/registration inside left area\n- Frontend user-information editing\n(Or are the last two things only possible with ur “Front-end Membership” Plugin?)\n\nAnd in addition one please when you have time:\nWhen its possible for you, plz test “Hide My WP” plugin and functions\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11722276" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello Steve, we are in process of re-writing this plugin with make it a complete support solution with rest api and mobile app etc. will include these features as well in upcoming versions.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Best Solutions for Support', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'best-solutions-for-support', '', '', '2016-01-19 03:49:27', '2016-01-19 03:49:27', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=458', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(460, 1, '2016-01-19 03:52:39', '2016-01-19 03:52:39', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>nanaboakye</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nPre-Sales Question:\n\nDo you have any plans of integrating live Chats and VoIP telephony APIs (e.g. Twilio)?\n\nI would love to have a complete customer support with ticketing, Live Chat &amp; Phone Support.\n\nSuch that Live and Phone chats can be converted to tickets\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11699720" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>nanaboakye</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nIs the author of this plugin serious at all with this product. So many requests not responded. I definitely will not waste 27 bucks for this\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11702404" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, I am in process of writing this plugin from scratch with all the requests from our existing customers. Such major upgrades take time however, I plan to release the new and improved version by end of December or Jan first week. Stay updated as this is going to be the best support app ever launched on Envato market, possibly with free Mobile app for staff and admins.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11702676" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>nanaboakye</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThanks for the response. Will any of these integration features be added to the plugin\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11722103" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nYes, that’s the plan, will try to release mobile app as well so agents can reply on the go.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11722458" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>nanaboakye</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI can’t wait to see these features in action. I will buy the product once these features make it to the plugin\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11725778" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nSure, keep a watch on updates and if you like then go for it.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Plans for Integrating Live Chats', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'plans-for-integrating-live-chats', '', '', '2016-01-19 03:52:39', '2016-01-19 03:52:39', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=460', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(462, 1, '2016-01-19 03:57:02', '2016-01-19 03:57:02', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>kilick</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\nPre-sale question:\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nIs it possible to run on private/password protected pages? I want it to use for my students, not for public use.\n\nSo, is it possible to make users on it? I want to make 1 agent (me) and 20 students. They need to login to add a ticket.\n\nPlease let me know. Your plugin looks great.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11722244" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello, password protection page feature won’t work on the support app page. Will try to include this feature in future.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Running on Password Pages', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'running-on-password-pages', '', '', '2016-01-19 03:57:02', '2016-01-19 03:57:02', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=462', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(464, 1, '2016-01-19 03:59:52', '2016-01-19 03:59:52', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>anphira</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nPre-Sale Questions:\n\nCan the new ticket form be customized to add/remove fields?\n\nIs there a way for guests to submit tickets? Ideally I’d like guests (people not logged in) to be able to submit a ticket and then later view the ticket by entering its ID number into a search form.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11722192" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, you can add/remove custom fields in the form and you can try this on a demo site at <a href="http://cssjockey.net./" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net.</a>\n\nGuest tickets are not supported with current version, however, we plan to include this feature in upcoming versions.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Viewing the Ticket By ID Number', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'viewing-the-ticket-by-id-number', '', '', '2016-01-19 03:59:52', '2016-01-19 03:59:52', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=464', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(466, 1, '2016-01-19 04:04:20', '2016-01-19 04:04:20', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>gd0g</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nPlease be aware this plugin is really like having a separate webpage. Whilst the description “sort of” says so the description to me is not crystal clear. So whislt you upload the plugin to your wordpress site it really acts indepenedent and is not part of your theme at all. Which maybe fine for some buyers. Just be aware that there is work involved to style the plugin to your branding and there will be limitations.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11722175" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nIts clearly mentioned within the first paragraph of plugin description.\n\n“SupportEzzy is an elegant support tickets system and scrs portal for WordPress. This is a stand-alone AngularJS app which runs on a single WordPress page of your website. This app does not interfere with your existing theme and plugins and will work with any kind of WordPress website.”\n\nPlease feel free to provide feedback on what kind of UI/UX you would expect in upcoming version. We are in process of re-writing the plugin from scratch with more features and themes.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Uploading The Plugin to Wordpress', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'uploading-the-plugin-to-wordpress', '', '', '2016-01-19 04:04:20', '2016-01-19 04:04:20', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=466', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(468, 1, '2016-01-19 04:07:56', '2016-01-19 04:07:56', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30"></div>\n<div class="comment__body"></div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"><strong> ericho09</strong></div>\n<div></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11722175" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item">\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nPre-sales questions: Regrading Email Piping and Routing: Does Ezzy and WP use same member database? When non-WP member submit a ticket to <a href="mailto:supportezzy@cssjockey.com">supportezzy@cssjockey.com</a>, will WP automatically register this non-WP member? I actually don’t want Ezzy to create a new user when a non-WP member submit a ticket. Do you have any Macro function, so ticket admin didn’t to write up everything for every single ticket.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11722088" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, this plugin uses same wp_users table to interact with user information. If someone sends an email which is not registered in the system, supportezzy will create a new account to assign the ticket to the user. Macros will be available in upcoming version as we are planning to replace the WYSIWYG editor with a better one.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11723393" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>ericho09</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThat may confuse user, isn’t it? When Ezzy automatic created a new account for a user, that user will be confused because he already register a WP account that he didn’t know. Do other workaround this problem??\n\nWhen you will release upcoming version?\n\nThank you.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11739703" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nNew User account only be created if the email address is not already registered. We plan to release the new version in Jan 2016.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11793282" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>ericho09</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nInterested to know what is the mobile app new feature is about? and what other new features that will release on Jan 2016?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11799121" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nWith mobile app, agents will be able to answer tickets on the go, will try to integrate the push notifications as well or at later stage. This software is being re-written from scratch which will use rest api which will enable us to integrate any kind of form being used to create tickets. There’s a long list of feature requests from our clients so we will be adding all these on priority basis.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response"></div>\n</div>', 'Email Piping and Routing', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'email-piping-and-routing', '', '', '2016-01-19 04:07:56', '2016-01-19 04:07:56', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=468', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(470, 1, '2016-01-19 04:16:41', '2016-01-19 04:16:41', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>zoom3d</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div>January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nhello, I want to congratulate the beautiful plugin, it’s perfect, but I have a doubt. How do I get the user to be redirected to the ticket page after login to the site? I found this option. I’m using the plugin CSSJockey Membership Modules\n\nCan you help me?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11739677" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">January 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThanks. You can set redirect url in login shortcode to the support page url and user will be sent to support app after they login.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11742539" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>zoom3d</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">January 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nand how to do it?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11750852" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nPlease refer to this page to learn more about login shortcode. <a href="http://docs.cssjockey.com/cjfm/login-form-shortcode/" rel="nofollow">http://docs.cssjockey.com/cjfm/login-form-shortcode/</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11754941" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><u><span style="color: #0066cc;"> </span></u></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>zoom3d </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nOn the previous question and I managed to solve this all right.\n\nBut now came a new question.\n\nI’m having problems sending and receiving files on tickets. The files are made without pronlemas more I get all the corrupted files. Because the files are getting corrupted?\n\nCould you help me?\n\nThanks,\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11754964" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>zoom3d </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI will leave here a note:\n\nThe files are being sent to the server in the / uploads and usually flawless, I downloaded the file and it opens normally.\n\nBut when I try to download the file from the tickets panel files are corrupted.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11758822" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, What’s the file extension?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11763650" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>zoom3d </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nExtensions | jpg | jpeg | bmp | png |They are coming normally. But extensions | zip | rar | pdf | doc | docx | They are coming corrupted.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11769183" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello, Please create a ticket at <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com</a> with temp WordPress admin account, so I can check and help you with the fix.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11771986" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>zoom3d </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nok, I sent a ticket for you\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Redirecting to the Ticket Page', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'redirecting-to-the-ticket-page', '', '', '2016-01-19 04:16:41', '2016-01-19 04:16:41', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=470', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0) ;
