(472, 1, '2017-01-19 04:26:30', '2017-01-19 04:26:30', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>jcev</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, I purchased the plugin and i am having problems setting it up. When a ticket is submitted the submitter gets an email alert that it has been submitted, but us the ones assigned the ticket do not get the email.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11788225" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, Please create a ticket at <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com</a> with temp WordPress admin account, so I can check the setup and help you with the fixes.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Email Error', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'email-error', '', '', '2017-01-19 04:26:30', '2017-01-19 04:26:30', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=472', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(474, 1, '2017-06-19 04:39:03', '2017-06-19 04:39:03', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>dtommy79</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n“Customers must verify their purchase before creating new tickets.”\n\nDoes this only apply to Envato products or you can generate a purchase code to other products as well?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11818573" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, this only works with envato products.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Verifying the Purchase', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'verifying-the-purchase', '', '', '2017-06-19 04:39:03', '2017-06-19 04:39:03', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=474', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(476, 1, '2016-01-19 04:39:32', '2016-01-19 04:39:32', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>tcibene</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nPre-sale question: If someone emails to start a ticket and adds an attachment to the email, does it automatically show up in the job ticket on the site?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11862423" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nyes, it does. Please try this plugin and features at <a href="http://cssjockey.net/" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net</a> to make sure it suits your needs.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Automatic Show Up', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'automatic-show-up', '', '', '2016-01-19 04:39:32', '2016-01-19 04:39:32', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=476', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(478, 1, '2016-01-19 04:50:39', '2016-01-19 04:50:39', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>Jonyb </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nAfter using for a while I now have this error\n\nFatal error: Cannot call overloaded function for non-object in public_html/support/wp-includes/functions.php on line 1420\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11862419" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nPlease create a ticket at <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com</a> with temp WordPress admin account, so we can check and help you with the fix.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Fatal Error', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'fatal-error', '', '', '2016-01-19 04:50:39', '2016-01-19 04:50:39', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=478', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(480, 1, '2016-01-19 04:55:08', '2016-01-19 04:55:08', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>dtommy79</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nAny chance you’ll add support for easy digital downloads?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11891792" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">January 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, we are in process of re-writing this plugin. We will consider this for sure as this has been requested by a few other customers as well.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11903344" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>dtommy79</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThanks\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Easy Digital Downloads', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', '480', '', '', '2016-01-19 04:55:08', '2016-01-19 04:55:08', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=480', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(483, 1, '2016-01-19 05:06:43', '2016-01-19 05:06:43', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>Philoveracity_Design</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n&nbsp;\n\nPre-Sales Question:\n\nYour app looks very nice but how can I be sure that one day you will not discontinue support and abandon this altogether?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11891843" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, We are in process of re-writing the plugin from scratch to use latest technologies and integrate all features requested by our clients.\n\nSales for these plugin are good and so far there’s no other plugin like this in the market. These are a few reasons we are making this even better and will continue support as per Envato policy.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Better Support as per Envato Policy', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'better-support-as-per-envato-policy', '', '', '2016-01-19 05:06:43', '2016-01-19 05:06:43', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=483', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(485, 1, '2016-01-19 05:15:26', '2016-01-19 05:15:26', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>ericho09</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI got “The uploaded file exceeds the upload_max_filesize directive in php.ini.” when I upload for my own theme or any plugins such as “Quform” and “UserPro”. How do I test my theme and plugins?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11909487" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>ericho09</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n2. How to sort by Department?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11970094" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>ericho09</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nforget the first. How to sort by Department? I didn’t see department on left side.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11975373" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/CSSJockey">CSSJockey</a></strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nYou see departments when you are logged in as admin or agent. Do check if products and departments are enabled under plugin settings.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Testing the Theme and Plugins', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'testing-the-theme-and-plugins', '', '', '2016-01-19 05:15:26', '2016-01-19 05:15:26', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=485', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(487, 1, '2016-01-19 05:25:19', '2016-01-19 05:25:19', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>Philoveracity_Design</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nPRE SALES QUESTION #2:\n\nIt appears that this plugin has not been updated as compatible with WordPress 4.4 The new version of WordPress that was released on December the 8th.\n\nSince the release of WordPress 4.4 was on December the 8th and the last actual update this plugin was September 2nd, 2015 I have actual concerns of compatibility and security.\n\nI am actually ready to buy the plugin but have legitimate concerns because I keep all of my WordPress installations and plugins up to date regularly and have clients who need this same regularity of updates.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11975274" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, this plugin is compatible with latest WordPress, you can try the same at <a href="http://cssjockey.net./" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net.</a> We are also re-writing this plugin from scratch with latest technology and APIs.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Plugins Not Updated', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'plugins-not-updated', '', '', '2016-01-19 05:25:19', '2016-01-19 05:25:19', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=487', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0)