(505, 1, '2015-12-19 06:53:52', '2015-12-19 06:53:52', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>jsmacdougall</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">December 2015</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nWould be so great if there could be a function to add multiple start and stop times to a ticket and then be able to print out a ticket to PDF for a report once completed.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11511891" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello, we will consider this in future versions, as, our main focus now is to optimise the current functionality of this plugin.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Function to Add Start and Stop', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'function-to-add-start-and-stop', '', '', '2015-12-19 06:53:52', '2015-12-19 06:53:52', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=505', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
