(520, 1, '2015-12-19 07:17:30', '2015-12-19 07:17:30', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>REDSCHOOL</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nDecember 2015\n\nPresale question. Any ETA on the next update with paying users management. I really like this plugin and would like to use it for 3 support pricing plans(free, standard, pro). Any news?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11494805" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>REDSCHOOL </strong></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nJust purchased the plugin. Its really great! But i have two support ticket on your helpdesk for 2 days: Ticket ID: E8LOAGL6482079 and Ticket ID: M5YWG0I9772078 . I realy need help with them!!!\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11511970" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello, sorry for the delay. I responded to your tickets today, please check and lets get this sorted.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'ETA on the Next Update', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'eta-on-the-next-update', '', '', '2015-12-19 07:17:30', '2015-12-19 07:17:30', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=520', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
(522, 1, '2015-12-19 07:21:40', '2015-12-19 07:21:40', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>josemanuel</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">December 2015</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi its possible to display on the sidebar departments and show all the tickets for that department?\n\nAnother questions:\n\n1. about the dynamic variables, when the user receive the notification email the url ticket will go to the frontend?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11542683" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nYes, departments list is available in the sidebar to fetch all tickets for selected departments.\n\nThe link in each mail sent by the system on ticket submission or comment will redirect the user to the ticket.\n\nPlease create your demo site at <a href="http://cssjockey.net/" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net</a> to check all features and see if that works as per your requirements.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Display on the Sidebars', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'display-on-the-sidebars', '', '', '2015-12-19 07:21:40', '2015-12-19 07:21:40', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=522', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0) ;
