(765, 1, '2016-06-14 10:45:44', '2016-06-14 10:45:44', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/websitecenter">websitecenter</a> </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">June 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello, I have sent you a ticket regarding a few issues I have had with the software. the last response was 4 days ago, could you help me with the “No files found” issue. It seems to be something that happens regularly with the plugin from what I see in this comment forum.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12976489" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/cjrupak">cjrupak</a> </strong></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">June 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nSorry, it took time to get back to you but your ticket has been replied now.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Few Issues rregardd', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '343-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-14 10:45:44', '2016-06-14 10:45:44', '', 343, 'http://127.0.0.1/343-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(766, 1, '2015-12-19 06:21:19', '2015-12-19 06:21:19', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>trec </strong></p>\nDecember 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nok i found another problem, when i go to main page for example as a client, there is on the left module QUICK LINKS, i have to open tickets but the number 2 doesnt appear, it only appears if I click any of these links. Why? It should appear on page load without any clicks.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11296717" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nDecember 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, Can you please enable debugging in App Configuration and share your website Url. You can also create a ticket at <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com./" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com.</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11300835" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><u><span style="color: #0066cc;"> </span></u></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>trec</strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI have sent you a message.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11309539" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nOk, will continue the conversation on our support portal.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Debugging in App Configuration', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '498-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-19 06:21:19', '2015-12-19 06:21:19', '', 498, 'http://127.0.0.1/498-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(767, 1, '2015-12-19 06:25:55', '2015-12-19 06:25:55', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>Elnooronline</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">December 2015</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nCan I translate the backend and change to right – left ? i have wordpress in arabic can i make this\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11371451" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">December 2015</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, this functionality isn’t available by default and not tested. You can try the plugin at <a href="http://cssjockey.net/" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net</a> and modify the CSS code via editor to see if it works as per your needs.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Translation', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '500-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-19 06:25:55', '2015-12-19 06:25:55', '', 500, 'http://127.0.0.1/500-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(768, 1, '2015-12-19 06:49:44', '2015-12-19 06:49:44', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>hellobusiness </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello, i have a problem with your system! When i press the submit ticket button, it is loading but nothing happens and stay there but the ticket has been created! It should move to another page, for example all tickets in order the user to know that the ticket has been succesfully created! What is wrong? How to solve that?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11343034" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, Can you please enable debugging under App Configuration and check if any errors shows up in Chrome Console.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11343074" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>hellobusiness </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI get some errors: <a href="http://i.imgur.com/tI4wgXs.png" rel="nofollow">http://i.imgur.com/tI4wgXs.png</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11343609" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><u><span style="color: #0066cc;"> </span></u></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>hellobusiness</strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nCan you help solve that bug?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11344610" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nPlease check if you have created departments and products under Tickets Admin Menu.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Debugging Under App Configuration', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '502-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-19 06:49:44', '2015-12-19 06:49:44', '', 502, 'http://127.0.0.1/502-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(769, 1, '2015-12-19 06:53:52', '2015-12-19 06:53:52', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>jsmacdougall</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">December 2015</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nWould be so great if there could be a function to add multiple start and stop times to a ticket and then be able to print out a ticket to PDF for a report once completed.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11511891" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello, we will consider this in future versions, as, our main focus now is to optimise the current functionality of this plugin.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Function to Add Start and Stop', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '505-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-19 06:53:52', '2015-12-19 06:53:52', '', 505, 'http://127.0.0.1/505-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
