(771, 1, '2015-12-19 07:00:43', '2015-12-19 07:00:43', '<strong>rezolution </strong>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHaving the same issue as @hellobusiness. There is no redirection happening after a user submits a ticket. The ticket is added to the department/product succcessfully. No errors come up in debug. So possibly redirection is not happening at all? Thanks\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11422386" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, Please create a ticket at <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com</a> with temp WordPress admin account and FTP account, so I can check the setup and help you with the fixes.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11422869" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>rezolution </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHI there..I just created a ticket on support Ticket ID: Z9VHIM638A1828 with logins. Thanks.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11542700" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, we replied to your ticket 7 days ago and today added a new comment to ping you via our support portal. Please check your email or login to our support portal <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com</a> to continue conversation via the ticket.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Redirecting is not Happening', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '509-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-19 07:00:43', '2015-12-19 07:00:43', '', 509, 'http://127.0.0.1/509-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
