(773, 1, '2015-12-19 07:07:30', '2015-12-19 07:07:30', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>farmanahmed</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">December 2015</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nIs there anyway I can add payment or membership to your ticket system plugin ? If not please let me know the alternatives\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11422369" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, this feature is currently not supported as part of this plugin however, you can use the hook to check if a user is paid user or not. Here’s the example code: <a href="https://github.com/cssjockey/supportezzy/blob/master/check-if-user-has-paid.php" rel="nofollow">https://github.com/cssjockey/supportezzy/blob/master/check-if-user-has-paid.php</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11422391" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><u><span style="color: #0066cc;"> </span></u></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>farmanahmed</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">December 2015</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI think you should allow this feature. I would like to have a support center for my clients if they register and pay monthly + the free version for 30 days as well. Please suggest any other plugin with these features\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11422403" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">December 2015</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, this feature will be added in upcoming version, this is temporary solution till the time this feature is included in the core with multiple payment gateways etc.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11422410" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>farmanahmed</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">December 2015</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nthankyou very much, I will be waiting for an update\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Adding Payment', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '514-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-19 07:07:30', '2015-12-19 07:07:30', '', 514, 'http://127.0.0.1/514-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
