(786, 1, '2016-01-15 07:44:11', '2016-01-15 07:44:11', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>wellsb</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI can seem to log into support ez using the admin login\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219271" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">January 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nUsers with admin account can login to the support portal.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Admin Account', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '435-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-15 07:44:11', '2016-01-15 07:44:11', '', 435, 'http://127.0.0.1/435-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(787, 1, '2016-01-16 15:13:33', '2016-01-16 15:13:33', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CrossLeaf</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nJanuary 2016\n\nWhat CSS script would I have to add to change the Green Buttons? In particular the most visible ones “Create New Ticket” “Transfer Ticket” “Post Response”\n\nThank you very much.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12399012" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThe class to change the green buttons is ’.btn-success’.\n\nJust add the following to our Custom CSS/Javascript page in the plugin settings:\n<h1>supportezzy .btn-success</h1>\n{ background-color: #your_color_code; border-color: #color_code_matching_the_bg_color; }\n\nCaution: It would change all the green buttons in the app.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Create New Ticket', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '446-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-16 15:13:33', '2016-01-16 15:13:33', '', 446, 'http://127.0.0.1/446-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(788, 1, '2016-01-16 15:16:12', '2016-01-16 15:16:12', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>stefan872 </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHow can i delete the unique code in the subject of the emails like this one: [SIW5WYI4BA102]\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12398934" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThis cannot be removed as it is needed to track tickets with IMAP.\n\nOtherwise, the comments on a ticket would be treated as a new and separate ticket.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Deleting Unique Code', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '448-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-16 15:16:12', '2016-01-16 15:16:12', '', 448, 'http://127.0.0.1/448-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(789, 1, '2016-01-16 15:21:46', '2016-01-16 15:21:46', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>franwess</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n&nbsp;\n\nJanuary 2016\n\nI have a pre-sales question related to a comment from a use above which I quote here:\n\n<em>“Question: If I assign a ticket to a group can I also assign it to an individual as well. For example: Ticket comes in – I assign it to System Group and I need to assign it my manager Jane Doe. If so, how?</em>\n<em>Hi, in current version assigning to an individual is not possible.”</em>\n\nDoes this mean that I can not assign tickets to individuals within a group or does it only mean that when assigned to a group, I cannot also assign to an individual? In other words, what I’m asking is whether tickets are assigned to individuals within groups or only to the group itself?\n\nIf I cannot assign to an individual, how are support agents held accountable?\n\nKind regards Francois Wessels\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12399343" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nIt is assigned to the individual inside a group (department).\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Assigning a Ticket', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '450-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-16 15:21:46', '2016-01-16 15:21:46', '', 450, 'http://127.0.0.1/450-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(790, 1, '2016-01-16 15:33:27', '2016-01-16 15:33:27', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>radioative</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi. My client can send an email to create a ticket or must login into the system do create one?\n\nI’d like to use this for customer support.\n\n1) My client send an email. (<a href="mailto:support@example.com">support@example.com</a>) 2) System converts this email to a ticket 3) I’ll use this system to respond and manage tickets. 4) When I respond, my client receive the response in email.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12399416" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nAny email sent to the set email address in the plugin settings under IMAP Configuration will be a new ticket and any replies to that email will be converted to comments.\n\nYou can try the plugin on <a href="http://cssjokcey.net/" rel="nofollow">http://cssjokcey.net</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Respond and Manage Tickets', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '452-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-16 15:33:27', '2016-01-16 15:33:27', '', 452, 'http://127.0.0.1/452-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(791, 1, '2016-01-19 03:46:23', '2016-01-19 03:46:23', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>sanderdatema</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI set one department and one product (because I don’t need them), but when you want to assign a ticket to another agent, the form still wants me to choose a department and product.\n\n1. Why ask if there’s no choice when there’s only on option? 2. Can it be turned off?\n\nThanks.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11722290" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThank you for your feedback, will sort this in upcoming version.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Assigning a Ticket', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '456-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 03:46:23', '2016-01-19 03:46:23', '', 456, 'http://127.0.0.1/456-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(792, 1, '2016-01-19 03:49:27', '2016-01-19 03:49:27', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>extensionforge </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\none of the best solutions for support/helpdesk I saw in the last years and thats one of the reasons to move from zendesk into my homepage.\n\nOne thing I’m wondering is – Is it possible to show the F.A.Q. inside the ticket system layout and not making a switch to the normal page-theme? Maybe I have tomatoes on my eyes : )\n\nAnd some featurewishes:\n- Statistics View\n- Option to add menue items\n- Frontend login/registration inside left area\n- Frontend user-information editing\n(Or are the last two things only possible with ur “Front-end Membership” Plugin?)\n\nAnd in addition one please when you have time:\nWhen its possible for you, plz test “Hide My WP” plugin and functions\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11722276" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello Steve, we are in process of re-writing this plugin with make it a complete support solution with rest api and mobile app etc. will include these features as well in upcoming versions.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Best Solutions for Support', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '458-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 03:49:27', '2016-01-19 03:49:27', '', 458, 'http://127.0.0.1/458-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(793, 1, '2016-01-19 03:52:39', '2016-01-19 03:52:39', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>nanaboakye</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nPre-Sales Question:\n\nDo you have any plans of integrating live Chats and VoIP telephony APIs (e.g. Twilio)?\n\nI would love to have a complete customer support with ticketing, Live Chat &amp; Phone Support.\n\nSuch that Live and Phone chats can be converted to tickets\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11699720" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>nanaboakye</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nIs the author of this plugin serious at all with this product. So many requests not responded. I definitely will not waste 27 bucks for this\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11702404" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, I am in process of writing this plugin from scratch with all the requests from our existing customers. Such major upgrades take time however, I plan to release the new and improved version by end of December or Jan first week. Stay updated as this is going to be the best support app ever launched on Envato market, possibly with free Mobile app for staff and admins.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11702676" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>nanaboakye</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThanks for the response. Will any of these integration features be added to the plugin\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11722103" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nYes, that’s the plan, will try to release mobile app as well so agents can reply on the go.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11722458" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>nanaboakye</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI can’t wait to see these features in action. I will buy the product once these features make it to the plugin\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11725778" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nSure, keep a watch on updates and if you like then go for it.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Plans for Integrating Live Chats', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '460-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 03:52:39', '2016-01-19 03:52:39', '', 460, 'http://127.0.0.1/460-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ;
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` ( `ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES
(794, 1, '2016-01-19 03:57:02', '2016-01-19 03:57:02', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>kilick</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\nPre-sale question:\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nIs it possible to run on private/password protected pages? I want it to use for my students, not for public use.\n\nSo, is it possible to make users on it? I want to make 1 agent (me) and 20 students. They need to login to add a ticket.\n\nPlease let me know. Your plugin looks great.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11722244" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello, password protection page feature won’t work on the support app page. Will try to include this feature in future.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Running on Password Pages', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '462-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 03:57:02', '2016-01-19 03:57:02', '', 462, 'http://127.0.0.1/462-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(795, 1, '2016-01-19 03:59:52', '2016-01-19 03:59:52', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>anphira</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nPre-Sale Questions:\n\nCan the new ticket form be customized to add/remove fields?\n\nIs there a way for guests to submit tickets? Ideally I’d like guests (people not logged in) to be able to submit a ticket and then later view the ticket by entering its ID number into a search form.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11722192" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, you can add/remove custom fields in the form and you can try this on a demo site at <a href="http://cssjockey.net./" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net.</a>\n\nGuest tickets are not supported with current version, however, we plan to include this feature in upcoming versions.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Viewing the Ticket By ID Number', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '464-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 03:59:52', '2016-01-19 03:59:52', '', 464, 'http://127.0.0.1/464-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(796, 1, '2016-01-19 04:04:20', '2016-01-19 04:04:20', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>gd0g</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nPlease be aware this plugin is really like having a separate webpage. Whilst the description “sort of” says so the description to me is not crystal clear. So whislt you upload the plugin to your wordpress site it really acts indepenedent and is not part of your theme at all. Which maybe fine for some buyers. Just be aware that there is work involved to style the plugin to your branding and there will be limitations.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11722175" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nIts clearly mentioned within the first paragraph of plugin description.\n\n“SupportEzzy is an elegant support tickets system and scrs portal for WordPress. This is a stand-alone AngularJS app which runs on a single WordPress page of your website. This app does not interfere with your existing theme and plugins and will work with any kind of WordPress website.”\n\nPlease feel free to provide feedback on what kind of UI/UX you would expect in upcoming version. We are in process of re-writing the plugin from scratch with more features and themes.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Uploading The Plugin to Wordpress', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '466-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 04:04:20', '2016-01-19 04:04:20', '', 466, 'http://127.0.0.1/466-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(797, 1, '2015-12-19 07:14:14', '2015-12-19 07:14:14', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>gxcdesign</strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nTrying to see the demo but the page does not load. thanks!\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11469927" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>gxcdesign </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI did go to <a href="http://demo.cssjockey.com/cjsupport/#/home" rel="nofollow">http://demo.cssjockey.com/cjsupport/#/home</a> and there was no demo there. Just loads and then a blank page with an orange header.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11511941" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello, you can try all our products by creating your own demo site at <a href="http://cssjockey.net./" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net.</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Page Does Not Load', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '518-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-19 07:14:14', '2015-12-19 07:14:14', '', 518, 'http://127.0.0.1/518-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(798, 1, '2015-12-19 07:17:30', '2015-12-19 07:17:30', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>REDSCHOOL</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nDecember 2015\n\nPresale question. Any ETA on the next update with paying users management. I really like this plugin and would like to use it for 3 support pricing plans(free, standard, pro). Any news?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11494805" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>REDSCHOOL </strong></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nJust purchased the plugin. Its really great! But i have two support ticket on your helpdesk for 2 days: Ticket ID: E8LOAGL6482079 and Ticket ID: M5YWG0I9772078 . I realy need help with them!!!\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11511970" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello, sorry for the delay. I responded to your tickets today, please check and lets get this sorted.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'ETA on the Next Update', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '520-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-19 07:17:30', '2015-12-19 07:17:30', '', 520, 'http://127.0.0.1/520-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(799, 1, '2015-12-19 07:21:40', '2015-12-19 07:21:40', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>josemanuel</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">December 2015</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi its possible to display on the sidebar departments and show all the tickets for that department?\n\nAnother questions:\n\n1. about the dynamic variables, when the user receive the notification email the url ticket will go to the frontend?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11542683" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nYes, departments list is available in the sidebar to fetch all tickets for selected departments.\n\nThe link in each mail sent by the system on ticket submission or comment will redirect the user to the ticket.\n\nPlease create your demo site at <a href="http://cssjockey.net/" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net</a> to check all features and see if that works as per your requirements.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Display on the Sidebars', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '522-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-19 07:21:40', '2015-12-19 07:21:40', '', 522, 'http://127.0.0.1/522-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(800, 1, '2015-12-19 07:24:58', '2015-12-19 07:24:58', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>rezolution </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nIve created 2 support tickets on your site and still not had any response for over a month.\n\nWe have a big issue with the Angular.js that we cannot resolve.\n\nWhen a ticket is submitted, the page refresh takes over 30 seconds. Users are not aware that the ticket has been submitted so continually click.\n\nWhy is the refresh taking so long -? And – why is my support taking so long?\n\nTicket ID: Z9VHIM638A1828\n\nPlease help asap.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11541574" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>rezolution</strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nStill nothing.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11542657" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello, please check your email or login to our support portal, we replied to your ticket 7 days ago and awaiting your response.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11542869" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>rezolution </strong></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nInstalled your new version.\n\nWhen submitting, the buttons are disabled, yes – but it doesn’t redirect. It just hangs.\n\nYou have to manually click open tickets to see the ticket listed.\n\nDisabling the submit buttons only fixed half the issue. The non-redirection still exists.\n\nPlease advise.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11551733" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>rezolution </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nReally want this plugin to work properly, but the Ajax is killing me. Has anyone else managed to workaround the issue with no redirection after the ticket is submitted?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11620196" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, This seems to be working on our end and we don’t have any other tickets open for this issue as of now.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Issue with the Angular', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '524-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-19 07:24:58', '2015-12-19 07:24:58', '', 524, 'http://127.0.0.1/524-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(801, 1, '2015-12-19 07:29:07', '2015-12-19 07:29:07', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>josemanuel</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">December 2015</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi its possible to see a report panel of the tickets and users, its posible to set roles and permisions ?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11620205" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, reports will be added in upcoming versions, however there are only two types of roles admin and agent. you can try this plugin at <a href="http://cssjockey.net/" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11620235" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><u><span style="color: #0066cc;"> </span></u></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>josemanuel</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">December 2015</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n8 days for that answer? ok\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11722359" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nApologies for the delay, we are in process of re-writing our plugins and schedule has been pretty tight.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11724227" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>josemanuel</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">December 2015</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\ntoo late thanks\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Possible to see a Report Panel', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '526-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-19 07:29:07', '2015-12-19 07:29:07', '', 526, 'http://127.0.0.1/526-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(802, 1, '2015-12-19 07:33:18', '2015-12-19 07:33:18', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>farmanahmed</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">December 2015</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI want to create a website like this with your plugin. <a href="http://wpmaintainer.com/join/" rel="nofollow">http://wpmaintainer.com/join/</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11620020" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><u><span style="color: #0066cc;"> </span></u></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHey, paid tickets is not available yet. However, you can accomplish this via hooks. Please check these code blocks <a href="https://github.com/cssjockey/supportezzy" rel="nofollow">https://github.com/cssjockey/supportezzy</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11621128" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><u><span style="color: #0066cc;"> </span></u></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>farmanahmed</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">December 2015</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-prefor