(803, 1, '2015-12-19 07:36:47', '2015-12-19 07:36:47', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>Jonyb </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nCan you check the tickets on your portal please\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11619973" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHey, Sorry for the delay, we have hired more staff to attend the tickets on time. Please look for updates.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Checking Tickets', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '530-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-19 07:36:47', '2015-12-19 07:36:47', '', 530, 'http://127.0.0.1/530-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(804, 1, '2015-12-19 07:38:43', '2015-12-19 07:38:43', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>teoooooooooo </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi guys! I do have the “no file found” problem and I wrote on your support page (<a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/#/ticket/2110)" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com/#/ticket/2110)</a> 4 days ago without any answer. Can you please help me? Thanks and have a nice day\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11619944" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello, sorry for the delay, We have replied to all the tickets, please check for the updates.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'No File Found Problem', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '532-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-19 07:38:43', '2015-12-19 07:38:43', '', 532, 'http://127.0.0.1/532-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(805, 1, '2015-12-19 07:41:12', '2015-12-19 07:41:12', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>2020media</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">December 2015</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nFeature question. Is it possible to search SCR and add to ticket during the add coment to ticket stage?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11619932" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nDecember 2015\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, this features is not available yet.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Search SCR and Add Ticket', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '534-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-12-19 07:41:12', '2015-12-19 07:41:12', '', 534, 'http://127.0.0.1/534-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(806, 1, '2016-02-15 06:57:40', '2016-02-15 06:57:40', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>jerweb</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nany news about update?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12033023" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nFebruary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHey, we are working on it. there’s a lot to do and we are trying our best to complete and test this new version asap.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Updates', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '412-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-15 06:57:40', '2016-02-15 06:57:40', '', 412, 'http://127.0.0.1/412-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(807, 1, '2016-02-15 07:09:00', '2016-02-15 07:09:00', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>wprangers</strong></p>\nFebruary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\ncongratulations CSSJockey for making such a useful plugin, i was planing to start my support system with ticksy.com but after looking at your plugin i have decided to go for my self hosted solution.\n\ni have gone through all previous comments and i can understand that you a have a long list of items for the new version.\n\ni need a support system with-in a month as i am planning to release my first theme on themeforest. can you please give an idea as by when you can release the latest version? so that i can plan my schedule.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219391" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, Sorry for the delay in reply. Its taking a little longer than expected as the list is pretty huge, I think it is going to take another month or so.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Useful Plugin', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '414-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-15 07:09:00', '2016-02-15 07:09:00', '', 414, 'http://127.0.0.1/414-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(808, 1, '2016-02-15 07:12:46', '2016-02-15 07:12:46', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>xbhj308dh</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">February 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello, works with the new WP version?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219361" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">February 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nYes, it does.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'New WP Version', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '416-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-15 07:12:46', '2016-02-15 07:12:46', '', 416, 'http://127.0.0.1/416-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(809, 1, '2016-02-15 07:18:53', '2016-02-15 07:18:53', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>phatmano </strong></p>\nFebruary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI see you are also the author of Paid Content Packages Subscriptions. How does SupportEzzy Ticket System work with Paid Content Packages Subscriptions? Do they integrate at all? The solution I am looking for is a paid subscription support system. The scenario is simple: users buy monthly subscriptions and gain access to a level of support according to membership they paid for.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219347" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, Yes we do have Paid Content Packages in our portfolio however, they are not linked with each other as of now. We are in process of re-creating our plugins from scratch which will have these features included.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Paid Content Packages Subscriptions', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '418-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-15 07:18:53', '2016-02-15 07:18:53', '', 418, 'http://127.0.0.1/418-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(810, 1, '2016-02-15 07:21:19', '2016-02-15 07:21:19', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>phatmano</strong></p>\nFebruary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nWhere’s the demo for sign up pricing tables? And are there different presets?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219327" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">February 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, paid tickets and pricing tables are not included with this plugin.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Demo for Signing Up', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '420-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-15 07:21:19', '2016-02-15 07:21:19', '', 420, 'http://127.0.0.1/420-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(811, 1, '2016-02-15 07:24:00', '2016-02-15 07:24:00', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>simplyd</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">February 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\ntrying to setup email piping… but getting the error:\n\nCould not connect to IMAP server, please check and try again.\n\nCan’t connect to xxxxxxxxx,993: Connection timed out\n\ni tried with and without tls port 143/993\n\nalso tried with mailserver hostname and ip address\n\nnothing works, i can login to the mail account seperately with the credentials i am putting in\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12159460" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>simplyd</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">February 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\ni purchased this 4 days ago, and have requested support but nothing… surely you should not be selling a product on here if you cannot support it?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219290" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHey, sorry for the delay in replies here. Please create a ticket at <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com</a> with temp admin account and email details.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Email Piping', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '422-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-15 07:24:00', '2016-02-15 07:24:00', '', 422, 'http://127.0.0.1/422-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(812, 1, '2016-02-15 07:27:07', '2016-02-15 07:27:07', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>Jawad96</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">February 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi there,\n\nThis appears to be a comprehensive support plugin. I have a pre sale question – I intend to use this alongside WooCommerce.\n\nIt says I am able to set this up on a new Wordpress installation. Preferably I would like to add it to a sub-domain of support.mysite.com and have it linked to my main site so when customers click on support if they are logged in already on my main site then they will also be logged in on the support site. Not only this but it should also be able to check for WooCommerce order history etc\n\nIs this possible?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219317" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, the login functions will work if it is a multisite install. However, Woocommerce needs to the on same site.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Woocommerce', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '425-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-15 07:27:07', '2016-02-15 07:27:07', '', 425, 'http://127.0.0.1/425-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(813, 1, '2016-02-15 07:29:40', '2016-02-15 07:29:40', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>BigStache</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">February 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nAfter logging into the demo site as a client it appears that I can see all tickets. Even from other clients? Is that correct? I would not want one client to see other clients tickets.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219309" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, I’d recommend you to test this plugin at <a href="http://cssjockey.net/" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net</a> as an admin. Create different accounts for agents and clients and setup the plugin the way you want to check if it meets your requirements.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Plugin Test', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '427-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-15 07:29:40', '2016-02-15 07:29:40', '', 427, 'http://127.0.0.1/427-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(814, 1, '2016-01-19 04:07:56', '2016-01-19 04:07:56', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30"></div>\n<div class="comment__body"></div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"><strong> ericho09</strong></div>\n<div></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11722175" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item">\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nPre-sales questions: Regrading Email Piping and Routing: Does Ezzy and WP use same member database? When non-WP member submit a ticket to <a href="mailto:supportezzy@cssjockey.com">supportezzy@cssjockey.com</a>, will WP automatically register this non-WP member? I actually don’t want Ezzy to create a new user when a non-WP member submit a ticket. Do you have any Macro function, so ticket admin didn’t to write up everything for every single ticket.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11722088" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, this plugin uses same wp_users table to interact with user information. If someone sends an email which is not registered in the system, supportezzy will create a new account to assign the ticket to the user. Macros will be available in upcoming version as we are planning to replace the WYSIWYG editor with a better one.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11723393" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>ericho09</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThat may confuse user, isn’t it? When Ezzy automatic created a new account for a user, that user will be confused because he already register a WP account that he didn’t know. Do other workaround this problem??\n\nWhen you will release upcoming version?\n\nThank you.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11739703" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nNew User account only be created if the email address is not already registered. We plan to release the new version in Jan 2016.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11793282" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>ericho09</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nInterested to know what is the mobile app new feature is about? and what other new features that will release on Jan 2016?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11799121" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nWith mobile app, agents will be able to answer tickets on the go, will try to integrate the push notifications as well or at later stage. This software is being re-written from scratch which will use rest api which will enable us to integrate any kind of form being used to create tickets. There’s a long list of feature requests from our clients so we will be adding all these on priority basis.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response"></div>\n</div>', 'Email Piping and Routing', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '468-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 04:07:56', '2016-01-19 04:07:56', '', 468, 'http://127.0.0.1/468-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ;
