(815, 1, '2016-01-19 04:16:41', '2016-01-19 04:16:41', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>zoom3d</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div>January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nhello, I want to congratulate the beautiful plugin, it’s perfect, but I have a doubt. How do I get the user to be redirected to the ticket page after login to the site? I found this option. I’m using the plugin CSSJockey Membership Modules\n\nCan you help me?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11739677" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">January 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThanks. You can set redirect url in login shortcode to the support page url and user will be sent to support app after they login.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11742539" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>zoom3d</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">January 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nand how to do it?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11750852" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nPlease refer to this page to learn more about login shortcode. <a href="http://docs.cssjockey.com/cjfm/login-form-shortcode/" rel="nofollow">http://docs.cssjockey.com/cjfm/login-form-shortcode/</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11754941" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><u><span style="color: #0066cc;"> </span></u></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>zoom3d </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nOn the previous question and I managed to solve this all right.\n\nBut now came a new question.\n\nI’m having problems sending and receiving files on tickets. The files are made without pronlemas more I get all the corrupted files. Because the files are getting corrupted?\n\nCould you help me?\n\nThanks,\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11754964" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>zoom3d </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI will leave here a note:\n\nThe files are being sent to the server in the / uploads and usually flawless, I downloaded the file and it opens normally.\n\nBut when I try to download the file from the tickets panel files are corrupted.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11758822" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, What’s the file extension?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11763650" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>zoom3d </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nExtensions | jpg | jpeg | bmp | png |They are coming normally. But extensions | zip | rar | pdf | doc | docx | They are coming corrupted.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11769183" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello, Please create a ticket at <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com</a> with temp WordPress admin account, so I can check and help you with the fix.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11771986" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>zoom3d </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nok, I sent a ticket for you\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Redirecting to the Ticket Page', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '470-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 04:16:41', '2016-01-19 04:16:41', '', 470, 'http://127.0.0.1/470-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(816, 1, '2016-01-19 04:39:32', '2016-01-19 04:39:32', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>tcibene</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nPre-sale question: If someone emails to start a ticket and adds an attachment to the email, does it automatically show up in the job ticket on the site?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11862423" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nyes, it does. Please try this plugin and features at <a href="http://cssjockey.net/" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net</a> to make sure it suits your needs.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Automatic Show Up', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '476-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 04:39:32', '2016-01-19 04:39:32', '', 476, 'http://127.0.0.1/476-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(817, 1, '2016-01-19 04:50:39', '2016-01-19 04:50:39', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>Jonyb </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nAfter using for a while I now have this error\n\nFatal error: Cannot call overloaded function for non-object in public_html/support/wp-includes/functions.php on line 1420\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11862419" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nPlease create a ticket at <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com</a> with temp WordPress admin account, so we can check and help you with the fix.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Fatal Error', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '478-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 04:50:39', '2016-01-19 04:50:39', '', 478, 'http://127.0.0.1/478-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(818, 1, '2016-01-19 04:55:08', '2016-01-19 04:55:08', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>dtommy79</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nAny chance you’ll add support for easy digital downloads?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11891792" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">January 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, we are in process of re-writing this plugin. We will consider this for sure as this has been requested by a few other customers as well.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11903344" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>dtommy79</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThanks\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Easy Digital Downloads', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '480-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 04:55:08', '2016-01-19 04:55:08', '', 480, 'http://127.0.0.1/480-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(819, 1, '2016-01-19 05:06:43', '2016-01-19 05:06:43', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>Philoveracity_Design</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n&nbsp;\n\nPre-Sales Question:\n\nYour app looks very nice but how can I be sure that one day you will not discontinue support and abandon this altogether?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11891843" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, We are in process of re-writing the plugin from scratch to use latest technologies and integrate all features requested by our clients.\n\nSales for these plugin are good and so far there’s no other plugin like this in the market. These are a few reasons we are making this even better and will continue support as per Envato policy.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Better Support as per Envato Policy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '483-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 05:06:43', '2016-01-19 05:06:43', '', 483, 'http://127.0.0.1/483-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(820, 1, '2016-01-19 05:15:26', '2016-01-19 05:15:26', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>ericho09</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI got “The uploaded file exceeds the upload_max_filesize directive in php.ini.” when I upload for my own theme or any plugins such as “Quform” and “UserPro”. How do I test my theme and plugins?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11909487" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>ericho09</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n2. How to sort by Department?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11970094" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>ericho09</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nforget the first. How to sort by Department? I didn’t see department on left side.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11975373" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/CSSJockey">CSSJockey</a></strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nYou see departments when you are logged in as admin or agent. Do check if products and departments are enabled under plugin settings.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Testing the Theme and Plugins', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '485-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 05:15:26', '2016-01-19 05:15:26', '', 485, 'http://127.0.0.1/485-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(821, 1, '2016-01-19 05:25:19', '2016-01-19 05:25:19', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>Philoveracity_Design</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nPRE SALES QUESTION #2:\n\nIt appears that this plugin has not been updated as compatible with WordPress 4.4 The new version of WordPress that was released on December the 8th.\n\nSince the release of WordPress 4.4 was on December the 8th and the last actual update this plugin was September 2nd, 2015 I have actual concerns of compatibility and security.\n\nI am actually ready to buy the plugin but have legitimate concerns because I keep all of my WordPress installations and plugins up to date regularly and have clients who need this same regularity of updates.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11975274" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, this plugin is compatible with latest WordPress, you can try the same at <a href="http://cssjockey.net./" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net.</a> We are also re-writing this plugin from scratch with latest technology and APIs.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Plugins Not Updated', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '487-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 05:25:19', '2016-01-19 05:25:19', '', 487, 'http://127.0.0.1/487-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(822, 1, '2016-01-19 05:33:03', '2016-01-19 05:33:03', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>Philoveracity_Design</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">January 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nDo you have an answer to my previous question?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_11975399" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, I’ve replied to your comments. Do let me know if you have any more questions.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Answer for the Question', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '489-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 05:33:03', '2016-01-19 05:33:03', '', 489, 'http://127.0.0.1/489-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(823, 1, '2016-01-19 05:35:11', '2016-01-19 05:35:11', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>Elgunk</strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello, I was going to buy it but you said new version is coming. When do you think it will come out? SHould I wait new version or I will be able to update easily from WP dashboard? Thanks\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12033043" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, new version is being built from ground up and we are trying our best to complete and test the same asap. We have plan to release the same by end of this month, however, it can be a little longer as well because the list of features we are adding is very very extensive..\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Update from WP Dashboard', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '491-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 05:35:11', '2016-01-19 05:35:11', '', 491, 'http://127.0.0.1/491-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(824, 1, '2016-01-19 05:41:03', '2016-01-19 05:41:03', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>dragonsflight</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nJanuary 2026\n\nI’m running version 1.4.2 and am having lots of issues with it. We thought we had installed the best, but can’t solve ongoing problems.\n\nFirst, every ticket is duplicated. When a ticket is created, we actually get 2 or 3 tickets that are identical.\n\nSecond, logging in is intermittent. when my support tech gets an email that there is a new ticket, they click the link in the notification email, it takes them to the web site log in page. We have to actually log in to the admin section, go back to the front page to click ‘Support’, load the support page and only after Reloading the support ticket page, can we see the tickets.\n\nWe have Wordpress 4.3 at this time.\n\nVery frustrated here. We are getting ready to search for another support ticket system.\n\nPlease help.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12033036" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nCan you please create a ticket at <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com</a> with temp WordPress admin account, so we can check and help you with the fix.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12033231" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>dragonsflight </strong></p>\nJanuary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI have and am waiting a reply. 6 days…\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Tickets are Duplicated', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '493-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 05:41:03', '2016-01-19 05:41:03', '', 493, 'http://127.0.0.1/493-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(825, 1, '2016-01-19 05:55:01', '2016-01-19 05:55:01', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>sp1nner</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nJanuary 2016\n\nI want to try and check your plugin but when I am trying to login as “Technical Support Agent” the password or username is not working anymore. Can I ask for the updated logins?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12033030" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">January 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHey, you can test the software at <a href="http://cssjockey.net/" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net</a> as admin, create accounts for clients and agents and test each feature..\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Technical Support Agents', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '495-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-01-19 05:55:01', '2016-01-19 05:55:01', '', 495, 'http://127.0.0.1/495-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(826, 1, '2016-05-14 07:51:29', '2016-05-14 07:51:29', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>EvoRod</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">May 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThe File Attachement doesnt send. i recive the email but without image .png and .jpg\n\nin case for (word) is doc ? correct ?\n\nThe Stars Rating doesnt work too.\n\ni have the last version\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13505295" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">May 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nPlease let us know the plugin version number you are using right now.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13508362" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>EvoRod</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">May 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nVersión 1.4.3\n\nThe attached file i saw when im going to answer a ticket on the sistem support portal, the attached file be on below the coment, but no recive too on the email notification\n\nthe rate star doesnt work too. i try on your demo and doesnt work the stars\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13535618" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">May 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nIf you are using our latest version then these issues should not appear.\n\nCan you please create a ticket on <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com/</a> so that we can securely share the website info and help you debug the issue.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Stars Rating Error', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '291-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-05-14 07:51:29', '2016-05-14 07:51:29', '', 291, 'http://127.0.0.1/291-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(827, 1, '2016-05-14 08:00:24', '2016-05-14 08:00:24', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>bildraumwest</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">May 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHey, is it possible to embed google tables via frame in a “ticket chat”?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13509697" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>bildraumwest</strong></p>\nMay 2016\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\niframe I mean\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13535663" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">May 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nSorry, iframes won’t work in the plugin.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response"></div>', 'Ticket Chat', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '294-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-05-14 08:00:24', '2016-05-14 08:00:24', '', 294, 'http://127.0.0.1/294-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(828, 1, '2016-04-15 05:38:02', '2016-04-15 05:38:02', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>eduardocs </strong></p>\nApril 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nWhen I open a ticket I do not receive my email notification…HELP!!!\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12488814" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\nApril 2016\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nIt can be a problem with the server or with mail SMTP settings. Can you please first take a look at the mail error logs on your server.\n\nIf everything seems fine, please open a ticket on our support portal at <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com/</a> and we will help you debug the issue.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Server Problem', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '385-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-04-15 05:38:02', '2016-04-15 05:38:02', '', 385, 'http://127.0.0.1/385-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(829, 1, '2016-04-15 05:43:54', '2016-04-15 05:43:54', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>thesoftwarepeople</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">Aoril 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nYour demo page isn’t working…it says error establishing database connection.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12583121" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">April 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThank you for notification, sorted the issue.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Demo Page Error', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '387-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-04-15 05:43:54', '2016-04-15 05:43:54', '', 387, 'http://127.0.0.1/387-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(830, 1, '2016-04-15 05:48:33', '2016-04-15 05:48:33', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>sanket2612</strong></p>\nApril 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nYour site is showing Error establishing database connection. Not even able to verify the plugin by entering the purchase code pls fix it ASAP…\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12559540" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">April 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">Sorry for the inconvenience.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nIt has been fixed now.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Error Establishing Database Connection', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '389-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-04-15 05:48:33', '2016-04-15 05:48:33', '', 389, 'http://127.0.0.1/389-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(831, 1, '2016-04-15 05:53:36', '2016-04-15 05:53:36', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>thesoftwarepeople</strong></p>\nApril 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI keep re-entering my purchase code and it will not acknowledge that its entered nor show any messages about its status.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12559571" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">April 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">Our site was facing some technical issues. We have fixed it now, please try again and if you still face an issue, you can open a ticket on our support portal at : <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com/</a></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Re-Entering the Purchase Code', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '391-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-04-15 05:53:36', '2016-04-15 05:53:36', '', 391, 'http://127.0.0.1/391-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(832, 1, '2016-04-15 05:57:59', '2016-04-15 05:57:59', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>bmxtraining</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">April 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nCan users add youtube video code in their support ticket?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12607902" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">June 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">The video embed code will not work in the support ticket.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nIt will not be converted to a video and the code itself would get displayed.\n\nThe links for the video would work and for the links, you can choose whether to open the link in the same window or a new window. This can be done by clicking on the link icon on the top of ticket editor.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12607942" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">April 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nOne more thing, if someone has posted a video embed link in the ticket the video will be displayed in the email response he would get.\n\nThis work in Gmail, not sure about other email providers.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12624637" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>bmxtraining</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">April 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nCould this be changed? I would like clients to paste a youtube link and have the video show in the ticket text body like native wordpress does it\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12629151" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">April 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nWe will be enhancing the Editor in our next release and our next version will be out probably in 2 months time.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Adding Youtube Video code', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '393-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-04-15 05:57:59', '2016-04-15 05:57:59', '', 393, 'http://127.0.0.1/393-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(833, 1, '2016-04-15 06:02:18', '2016-04-15 06:02:18', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>janxcode</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">April 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, I have purchased the plugin, now i need to make clients register with envato item purchase code. How i can achieve that?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12644853" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">April 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">We cannot register clients with Envato Purchase code, however if you enable Envato Marketplace Integration from the plugin settings, after the ticket submission plugin would let you know if the client is a verified customer or not.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Register with Envato', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '395-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-04-15 06:02:18', '2016-04-15 06:02:18', '', 395, 'http://127.0.0.1/395-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(834, 1, '2016-03-15 06:11:02', '2016-03-15 06:11:02', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>HeeHA</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"> March 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI would like to use a member plugin for our members.\n\nUser Profiles Made Easy plugin <a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/user-profiles-made-easy-wordpress-plugin/4109874">http://codecanyon.net/item/user-profiles-made-easy-wordpress-plugin/4109874</a>Is it integrate the member system?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12644920" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">March 2016</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n&nbsp;\n\nWe haven’t tested our plugin with User Profiles Made Easy but I don’t think it would be a problem to use any plugin that helps you create user profiles.\n\nAs our plugin uses the default WordPress user’s base and it doesn’t matter from where or which platform the user has registered to login into the support portal as long as the user is registered in WordPress user’s table.\n\nStill if you have doubts you can test our plugin and the User Profile Made Easy plugin together on <a href="http://cssjockey.net/" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net/</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Member Plugin', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '397-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-15 06:11:02', '2016-03-15 06:11:02', '', 397, 'http://127.0.0.1/397-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(835, 1, '2016-03-15 06:30:56', '2016-03-15 06:30:56', '&nbsp;\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>thrempel</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">March 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nPre sale questions:\n\nI have tested the demo site, and i can’t upload files (even if they are smaller than 5mb), any bug or is just with the demo?\n\nCan i upgrade the files maximum size?\n\nCan i change, or create custom fields for the new ticket area?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12655735" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">March 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">1. It must be the demo site only, you can try the file upload on our live support portal by creating a demo ticket at <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com/</a></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n2. The maximum size depends on the maximum size specified for the WordPress. So it would be equal to whatever upload size has been set for the WordPress installation and you can change the text 5MB to anything.\n\n3. We cannot change the default fields on creating new ticket area but we can add custom fields to it.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Upgrade the Files', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '401-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-15 06:30:56', '2016-03-15 06:30:56', '', 401, 'http://127.0.0.1/401-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(836, 1, '2016-03-15 06:46:19', '2016-03-15 06:46:19', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>fidraman</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">March 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello Is this plugin RTL ready ? and can I add a map field in the ticket form ? so the admin can know exactly where is the problem in the map. Thank you\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12655854" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">March 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">RTL is not supported in this version but we will try and add RTL support in our next update.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nAre we talking about Google Maps? I am not able to get exactly what this map field would do? as we certainly can add custom fields to the new ticket form. Can you elaborate more on this map field?\n\nYou can also test our plugin at <a href="http://cssjockey.net/" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net/</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12657660" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>fidraman</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">March 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThank you for the quick replay. 1 – I hope the RTL support will come out as soon as possible so I can purchase it and use as my official support ticket. 2 – about the map field, yes it’s about google maps, the user can put the location pin anywhere in the map, and when apply the form, I, as an admin, I can see the same location in google map in the form along with other information .. 3- the user interface is it in the frond end of the WordPress setup (can it be in a page or a post ?) or in the back-end ? 4 – one more thing please, Is the user have to sign up in the website in order to submit a ticket ? Thank you a bunch.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12677358" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">March 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">The map feature is not available in right now but I think this is a good feature to add. We will consider it and try our best to include this in our next update but no promises though as adding a feature like this takes a lot’s of consideration and time to incorporate.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nYes, the user has to sign-in in order to submit a ticket as this app was created keeping in mind to give support to premium customers/clients and not to make it as a public forum.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Plugin RTL', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '404-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-15 06:46:19', '2016-03-15 06:46:19', '', 404, 'http://127.0.0.1/404-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(837, 1, '2016-03-15 06:49:29', '2016-03-15 06:49:29', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>exisadmin</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">March 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello, Is it possible to have different client groups (e.g. moms and dads) that can views different categories to address their tickets?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12677392" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">March 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">The tickets can be grouped only by the following:</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n1. Status (Open, Close, Awaiting Response &amp; Public) 2. Departments. 3. Products.\n\nOther than those I am afraid we cannot have any other group or groups to categorize the tickets.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Different Client Groups', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '406-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-15 06:49:29', '2016-03-15 06:49:29', '', 406, 'http://127.0.0.1/406-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ;
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` ( `ID`, `post_author`, `post_date`, `post_date_gmt`, `post_content`, `post_title`, `post_excerpt`, `post_status`, `comment_status`, `ping_status`, `post_password`, `post_name`, `to_ping`, `pinged`, `post_modified`, `post_modified_gmt`, `post_content_filtered`, `post_parent`, `guid`, `menu_order`, `post_type`, `post_mime_type`, `comment_count`) VALUES
(838, 1, '2016-03-15 06:51:18', '2016-03-15 06:51:18', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>TheChrisLusk</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">March 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThe ONLY thing lacking is a robust reporting tool. From the admin area is there a way to export all the tickets to a CSV file? I want to see how many tickets have been opened in each category or product by which clients, etc.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12712565" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">March 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">We already have a good Reporting Tool for the admin area in our development pipeline.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nRight now we cannot export tickets to a CSV file but for, now maybe you can use some other plugin that imports post data with comments, categories, etc… in a CSV file, as tickets are created as a custom post type with the name Tickets and the comments on the ticket are saved as WordPress Comments of that particular post(ticket).\n\nWe will give this feature in our next update.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12981540" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>TheChrisLusk</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">March 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThanks for the heads up. We are willing to pay for this as a separate plugin because we need it so badly.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Robust Reporting Tool', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '408-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-15 06:51:18', '2016-03-15 06:51:18', '', 408, 'http://127.0.0.1/408-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(839, 1, '2016-03-15 06:54:14', '2016-03-15 06:54:14', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>eddieneg</strong></p>\nMarch 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, I just wanted to seknow if the Ticket could be exported as a pdf so it can also be used as a tangible paper ticket?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12712636" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/cjrupak">c</a>jrupak</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">March 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">Unfortunately, in this version we cannot export a ticket to PDF.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Ticket Export as PDF', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '410-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-15 06:54:14', '2016-03-15 06:54:14', '', 410, 'http://127.0.0.1/410-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(840, 1, '2016-02-15 07:32:02', '2016-02-15 07:32:02', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>TheChrisLusk</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThis is probably one of the best plugins, BY FAR, on Envato! Really great job guys.\n\nFEEDBACK: Give labels and input groups classes or ID’s so they can be hidden easier (such as the URL box and priority) with CSS, or give an option to hide these since they are not required.\n\nQUESTION: How can I include my custom fields in the email messages?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219300" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/CSSJockey">CSSJockey</a> </strong></p>\nFebruary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThank you for your feedback, we will sort this in upcoming versions. Currently it is not possible to include the user input into email messages, however, we will include this option as well.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12236133" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>TheChrisLusk</strong></p>\nFebruary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nCool, any idea when this will be available? Pretty important to know the custom fields which is why we added them <img title=":)" src="https://codecanyon.net/images/smileys/happy.png" alt=":)" />\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12287624" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nWe are working hard to roll out the new version as soon as possible, however the list of features is pretty long and it will take us at least another month to roll out the new version.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13367631" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>TheChrisLusk</strong></p>\nFebruary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nChecking to see if the latest update had the possibility to include the custom fields in the notification emails? It seems useless to create a custom field and then not be able to send that data in the ticket email….right?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Best Plugins', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '429-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-15 07:32:02', '2016-02-15 07:32:02', '', 429, 'http://127.0.0.1/429-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(841, 1, '2016-02-15 07:39:43', '2016-02-15 07:39:43', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>Harlock_</strong></p>\nFebruary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, I need to offer ticket support for a woocommerce product but I need it to end after a determined period (i.e. a week). Is it possible? Thanks, Francesco\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219285" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, it is not possible as the system doesn’t trigger any such action. You need to keep track of time.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Ticket Support', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '431-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-15 07:39:43', '2016-02-15 07:39:43', '', 431, 'http://127.0.0.1/431-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(842, 1, '2016-03-15 07:41:50', '2016-03-15 07:41:50', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>wellsb</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">March 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nQuestion: If I assign a ticket to a group can I also assign it to an individual as well. For example: Ticket comes in – I assign it to System Group and I need to assign it my manager Jane Doe.\n\nIf so, how?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12219275" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">March 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, in current version assigning to an individual is not possible.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Assigning Tickets', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '433-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-15 07:41:50', '2016-03-15 07:41:50', '', 433, 'http://127.0.0.1/433-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(843, 1, '2016-02-16 14:43:32', '2016-02-16 14:43:32', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/iqit-commerce">iqit-commerce</a></strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">February 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThere is 500 internal error when i try do create test demo after receiving link on mail\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12264516" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>iqit-commerce</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">February 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nbtw I saw you working on new update, do you have any timeline? becouse if it will be near future i will probably wait for new update with mu support system change\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12287608" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nFebruary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, I’ll check the demo site and fix any issues this week. New version will take some time as the list