(844, 1, '2016-02-16 15:02:18', '2016-02-16 15:02:18', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>abokamel</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, iam interesting to purchase this plugin but i have some queries: RTL well supported or no? user can reply via email or no? in email notification could i put the sender email anything like <a href="mailto:support@mywebsite.com">support@mywebsite.com</a> ? thanks\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12287596" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">February 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, RTL is not fully tested, however, you can test this plugin and all its features at <a href="http://cssjockey.net./" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net.</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'RTL Support', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '442-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-16 15:02:18', '2016-02-16 15:02:18', '', 442, 'http://127.0.0.1/442-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(845, 1, '2016-02-16 15:07:45', '2016-02-16 15:07:45', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>brianoneill</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">February 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI am looking at the demo. When I click on SCR nothing happens? I am looking a ticket and knowledge base system, can you product do public SCR? If yes can you give me a link to a working demo?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12399079" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nFebruary 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi,\n\nHave you tried it on <a href="http://cssjockey.net/?" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net?</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Knowledge Base System', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '444-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-16 15:07:45', '2016-02-16 15:07:45', '', 444, 'http://127.0.0.1/444-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(846, 1, '2016-06-14 06:49:37', '2016-06-14 06:49:37', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>timesoftimes</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">June 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nis it possible to create custom status ?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"><strong>cjrupak</strong></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13291223" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">June 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nNot in this version but we will try and include this feature in our next version.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13291234" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><strong>timesoftimes</strong></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">June 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nwhen we will expect ?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13291257" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><strong>cjrupak </strong></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">June 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nProbably within next month.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13291272" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><strong>timesoftimes</strong></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n\nJune 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">i sent PM, kindly check it and reply me</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13291296" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">June 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nWhere have you send it, to what address?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13291303" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><strong>timesoftimes</strong></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">June 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nsent via your profile\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13291394" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><strong>cjrupak </strong></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">June 2016</div>