(897, 1, '2016-08-14 05:11:21', '2016-08-14 05:11:21', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>thesoftwarepeople</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">August 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI really would like a refund for my purchase. I just tried to leave a support ticket on your website and the error message says “Error Establishing Database Connection”. That error message has been the theme of my usage of the plugin. It was totally unusable and I would like my credits. I know more than 24hrs have passed but there was no way I could continue to use this without sacrificing using other plugins on the site. Issues included:\n\n- Plugin would prevent other plugins from sending email (ie Contact Form 7, sends notification email but wont send autoresponder email with your plugin active) - Users could not scroll ticket comments - Your plugin activation caused some plugin features on left admin menu to disappear.\n\nAnd given a refund, you wont have to worry about me still using the plugin, I cant use it now. Thanks\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_14114912" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><strong>cjrupak</strong></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">August 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">Can you please raise a refund request from your Envato Dashboard.</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Error Establishing Database Connection', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '254-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-14 05:11:21', '2016-08-14 05:11:21', '', 254, 'http://127.0.0.1/254-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(898, 1, '2016-08-14 05:16:12', '2016-08-14 05:16:12', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>zibaloon2 </strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">August 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello I updated .po file and I can see my translation when I was login, But when I logout can not see my translation and see original words.\n\n<strong>Cjrupak</strong>\n\nAugust 2016\n\nCan you please create a ticket at <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com/</a> so that we can get site details and help you debug the issue.\n\n</div>\n</div>', 'Translation Error', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '256-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-14 05:16:12', '2016-08-14 05:16:12', '', 256, 'http://127.0.0.1/256-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(899, 1, '2016-08-14 05:19:40', '2016-08-14 05:19:40', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>AlekseyZhdanov</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">August 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nDemo does not work.\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">August 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nWe’ve fixed our demo installs.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Demo Error', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '258-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-14 05:19:40', '2016-08-14 05:19:40', '', 258, 'http://127.0.0.1/258-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(900, 1, '2016-07-14 09:19:57', '2016-07-14 09:19:57', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>mike777 </strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">July 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHow can i make the SCR public.. means users should be able to view without registering.. THX in advance\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13674471" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\nJuly 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n&nbsp;\n\nIf we talk about the in-built functionality for SCR’s in the plugin, then it is not possible to view SCR’s without logining in.\n\nHowever, you can give a link for you SCR’s page in the description on the homepage of the ticket.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'SCR Public', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '313-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-14 09:19:57', '2016-07-14 09:19:57', '', 313, 'http://127.0.0.1/313-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(901, 1, '2016-07-14 09:28:07', '2016-07-14 09:28:07', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/extensionforge">extensionforge</a> </strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">July 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\njust for information. When I make a search-engine search and it shows the link to the support-portal the excerpt looks like:\n\n{ lang.quick_links }}. {{ lang.response_required }} {{ number_response_required }}; {{ lang.all_open_tickets }} {{ number_open_tickets }}; {{ lang.starred_tickets }...\n\nMaybe you implement a meta-description field or let is auto set the main-information.\n\nCheers,\nSteve\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13676895" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/extensionforge">extensionforge</a> </strong></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">July 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">BTW: <a href="https://www.google.de/search?sclient=psy-ab&amp;site=&amp;source=hp&amp;btnG=Suche&amp;q=http%3A%2F%2Fsupport.cssjockey.com" rel="nofollow">https://www.google.de/search?sclient=psy-ab&amp;site=&amp;source=hp&amp;btnG=Suche&amp;q=http%3A%2F%2Fsupport.cssjockey.com</a>Here you can see what inside the desciption happens.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13701143" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/cjrupak">cjrupak</a></strong></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">July 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThank you for the info. We will look into it and find a way to fix this.\n\nBest Regards, CSSJockey\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13701207" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/extensionforge">extensionforge</a> </strong></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">July 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nGreat : )\n\nHave a relaxed start into the week,\nSteve\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Search-Engine Search', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '316-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-14 09:28:07', '2016-07-14 09:28:07', '', 316, 'http://127.0.0.1/316-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(902, 1, '2016-07-14 09:31:32', '2016-07-14 09:31:32', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/GeniusLab">GeniusLab</a></strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"> July 2017</p>\n\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nI’m going on my holiday soon; and would like my customers to know ticket response time is delayed due to that. Is there an easy of adding a notice on top ‘Holiday from .. until .. ’ for example. Or do you have another tip? Many thanks in advance.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_13701334" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><strong><a class="t-link -decoration-reversed" href="https://codecanyon.net/user/cjrupak">cjrupak</a></strong></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">July 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nUnfortunately, we do not have a holiday notice or response module in the current version but the good news is that this module is in our pipeline for future updates down the line.\n\nFor the now the best you can do is add some text in the Emails that are sent when a tickets is created or commented by customizing the email templates from our Customize Email Messages section in the plugin settings.\n\nOr, you can put a highligted text on the homepage of the ticket portal, when the user is not logged in.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Ticket Response Time', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '318-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-14 09:31:32', '2016-07-14 09:31:32', '', 318, 'http://127.0.0.1/318-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(903, 1, '2016-06-15 05:30:39', '2016-06-15 05:30:39', '&nbsp;\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>jacklee2</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">June 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi there , Can i know this plugin allow Admin to manage the ticket ?? Example Admin can be see the report for support agent conversation with client and how the performance with the staff ?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12455865" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>jacklee2</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">June 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nAnd can i know the ticket able to be private ?? mean only the client and support agent able to see .\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12466071" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">June 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n1. The Admin would be able to manage tickets. He can also create a new ticket from the WordPress dashboard even. We right now do not have an extensive reporting section in this plugin but the admin can check the tickets and the comments on it in the backend and judge the performance.\n\n2. Yes, the tickets are totally private and only the agent to whom the product has been assigned will be able to see the tickets related to that product &amp; client will only be able to see his ticket unless marked as public.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Managing the Plugin', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '378-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-15 05:30:39', '2016-06-15 05:30:39', '', 378, 'http://127.0.0.1/378-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(904, 1, '2016-06-15 05:33:44', '2016-06-15 05:33:44', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>jerweb </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">June 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nJust wondering if there is Any ETA on new version have a project which still cannot go online and really waiting on update\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12466078" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">June 2016</p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">You can expect the new version of this plugin in 2 months time. Somewhere around the end of April.</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'ETA Update', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '381-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-15 05:33:44', '2016-06-15 05:33:44', '', 381, 'http://127.0.0.1/381-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(905, 1, '2016-06-15 05:35:43', '2016-06-15 05:35:43', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>marianstancu</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">June 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHello! Very nice plugin, congratulations! But! So slow!!!! Something is not right, I think. I try this on two powerful servers, but still slow… Is it possible to do something about that?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_12488797" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">June 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n&nbsp;\n\nHave you tried deactivating other plugins or test it on a default WordPress theme.\n\nIt can be a conflict issue while loading plugin resources.\n\nYou can also try some cache plugin(s) to speed up the process.\n\nIf none works, please open a ticket on our support portal at <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/" rel="nofollow">http://support.cssjockey.com/</a> and we will look into it.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Slow Process', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '383-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-06-15 05:35:43', '2016-06-15 05:35:43', '', 383, 'http://127.0.0.1/383-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(906, 1, '2016-10-12 07:30:51', '2016-10-12 07:30:51', '<b>sam6onzalez</b>\n\n<b> </b>October 2016\n\nPre-buy question. Are you able to create custom fields for the tickets?\n\n<b>CSSJockey</b><b>    </b>\n\nOctober 2016\n\nYes, you can. Please try the demo at <a href="http://cssjockey.net/">http://cssjockey.net</a>\n\n<b>sam6onzalez</b>\n\nOctober 2016\n\nnot reseting after submit\n\n<b>sam6onzalez</b>\n\nOctober 2016\n\nPlease ignore that… Typing in a different thread', 'Creating Custom Fields for Tickets', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '137-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-12 07:30:51', '2016-10-12 07:30:51', '', 137, 'http://127.0.0.1/137-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(907, 1, '2016-10-12 07:38:01', '2016-10-12 07:38:01', '<b>macoleco</b>\n\nOctober 2016\n\nIt has option to open a tickt without this logged in word press? But that is required insrir name and email? Wait …\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nOctober 2016\n\nNo, we cannot open a ticket without logging in.\n\n&nbsp;', 'Option to Open a New Ticket', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '141-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-12 07:38:01', '2016-10-12 07:38:01', '', 141, 'http://127.0.0.1/141-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(908, 1, '2016-09-12 09:22:03', '2016-09-12 09:22:03', '<b>connectus</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n<ol>\n 	<li>is this open source? We want the ability to link our database so user do not need to register again, to log a ticket?</li>\n 	<li>can we replied to existing ticket via email?</li>\n 	<li>can we get notification via email for new ticket, new reply from agent/client, ticket closed/re-opened?</li>\n 	<li>Does it have canned response?</li>\n 	<li>Does it required wordpress or can we install without it?</li>\n</ol>\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nThis is not open source but once purchased you are free to edit as you may as the code is not encrypted or anything.\n<ol>\n 	<li>You can reply via email but we recommend only to create a new ticket via email and the replies must be via logging in into the system.</li>\n 	<li>Yes, you will get all the notification and you can also customize the email text for the same.</li>\n 	<li>Canned responses are not working in this version, we will fix it in another version.</li>\n 	<li>It requires WordPress.</li>\n</ol>\n&nbsp;', 'Canned Response', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '186-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-12 09:22:03', '2016-09-12 09:22:03', '', 186, 'http://127.0.0.1/186-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(909, 1, '2016-09-12 09:25:26', '2016-09-12 09:25:26', '<b>   KPR</b>\n\n<b>  </b>September 2016\n\nJust bought, thanks for all your help Mohit and CJ!!\n\n<b>cjrupak</b><b>    </b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nThank you for considering and buying our product and you are most welcome.', 'Thanking', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '189-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-12 09:25:26', '2016-09-12 09:25:26', '', 189, 'http://127.0.0.1/189-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(910, 1, '2016-09-12 09:27:01', '2016-09-12 09:27:01', '<b>royalde</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nI have three issues.\n\nFirst: I would like know if it’s possible to sort products by hierarchy like:\n\nPants - Pants a - Pants b - Pants c\n\nT Shirt - T Shirt a - T Shirt b\n\nTennis - Tennis a - Tennis b\n\nOr if possible, would be even better, When select a parent category, show other select with products of the children category.\n\nSecond: When we transfer the ticket, we have to select the product again. It’s possible to leave filled, the product field in the ticket?\n\nThird: We need all the tickets are open to a specific User (manager / team coordinator). Is not good for us, tickets be randomly distributed among the users. Is it possible to set a default User to receive all open tickets?\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nTo sort the categories/products we would need to customize or alter few lines of code in the plugin.\n<ol>\n 	<li>No, the product fields has to be filled each time but we will try and give this option in a future update.</li>\n 	<li>You can select a user for all products and departments by clicking on Assign Products and Departments button under Manage Support Staff menu. There should be only one user to whom all the products are assigned and then he can distribute the tickets to other agents manually as per need.</li>\n</ol>', 'Specific User', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '191-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-12 09:27:01', '2016-09-12 09:27:01', '', 191, 'http://127.0.0.1/191-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(911, 1, '2016-09-12 09:30:00', '2016-09-12 09:30:00', '<b>Probewise</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nJust bought the plugin. I’ve found a bug that purchase code can be reused multiple times, just tested it with your support forum with two user account I’ve created. I’ve also found out that you are using old API/Legacy API for verification, it might be good if the new API is supported.\n\nMay I suggest to fix this issue and add a feature that purchase code should be stored at the database. It would be nice if there’s a back-end list of purchase code of customers and support remaining months. Check this plugin: https://codecanyon.net/item/smart-bbpress-nverify/6370189\n\nI hope you could reply soon, because this is a big issue for Envato authors like me.\n\n<b>CSSJockey </b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nThank you for the feedback. We are implementing new Envato API with the new version (currently in development) and integrating more features as well around this.\n\n<b>Probewise</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nThank you for your response. I hope to see those updates soon, especially for Envato verification to limit license code per user and to monitor support remaining months.\n\n<b>Probewise</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nI just want to ask, when will the new version of the plugin be released? I haven’t use your plugin since I bought it, just tested in on localhost because of the bug/issue that I have reported one week ago. If the update will take a long time, it’s better to get a refund and I’ll use my old support forum system instead of your plugin.\n\n<b>CSSJockey </b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nthe new version will take at least a month as we are re-writing it from scratch.\n\n<b>Probewise</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nThank you for your response, hope to see the update soon.', 'Purchased Plugin', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '193-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-12 09:30:00', '2016-09-12 09:30:00', '', 193, 'http://127.0.0.1/193-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(912, 1, '2016-09-12 09:31:35', '2016-09-12 09:31:35', '<a href="https://mzl.la/2cj9Vyn"> </a>\n\n<b>extensionforge</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nI set up Content Security Policy (CSP) and end up with that language file is not loading -&gt; http://bit.ly/2bXDbqN\n\nI set up the CSP with wildcart so everything have to load, but it doesn’t. Can u reproduse this issiue? CSP is necessary now so it would be great when u get into this: <a href="https://mzl.la/2cj9Vyn">https://mzl.la/2cj9Vyn</a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nSeptember 2017\n\n&nbsp;\n\nYour support page is not working because you are using minifier on the support page like CloudFlare or something else.\n\nOnce you will un-minify everything, it should work. If not then please create a ticket at : <a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/">http://support.cssjockey.com/</a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>extensionforge</b>\n\n<b>    </b>September 2016\n\n&nbsp;\n\nI changed nothing on my setup only the CSP thing inside the htaccess. I only use google pagespeed on the server but it workes the whole time.\n\nI setup the question in ur suport-portal so we can go deeper into it.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\n&nbsp;\n\nCan you please get me the ticket ID, so that i can see if it has been commented on<b>.</b>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>extensionforge</b>\n\n<b>    </b>September 2016\n\n&nbsp;\n\nthx for getting back to this. I was on vacation, I didn’t start a ticket right now, but will do this week, when I made more checks with the problem.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>extensionforge</b>\n\n<b>    </b>September 2016\n\nthere it is: 3182\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nThank you. We have received your ticket and will get back to you as soon as possible.\n\n<a href="http://support.cssjockey.com/"> </a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b> </b>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b> </b>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b> </b>\n\n<b>    </b>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;', 'Content Security Policy', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '195-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-12 09:31:35', '2016-09-12 09:31:35', '', 195, 'http://127.0.0.1/195-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(913, 1, '2016-09-12 09:44:15', '2016-09-12 09:44:15', '<b>seteoito</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nComments are not appearing on the panel, how do I solve?\n\n<b>CSSJockey</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nPlease create a ticket at http://support.cssjockey.com with temp WordPress admin account, so we can check and help you with the fix.', 'Temp', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '198-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-12 09:44:15', '2016-09-12 09:44:15', '', 198, 'http://127.0.0.1/198-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(914, 1, '2016-09-12 09:46:32', '2016-09-12 09:46:32', '<b>newthink_iran</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nI have a question. Imagine we have several departments. When a user clicks on a certain button, I want to open ticket page and an certain department is selected, Without the user chooses it. Is it possible in this plugin?\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nI am afraid this is not possible as of now in this version. Maybe we will include this in one of our future updates.', 'Open Ticket Page', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '200-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-12 09:46:32', '2016-09-12 09:46:32', '', 200, 'http://127.0.0.1/200-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(915, 1, '2016-09-12 09:47:46', '2016-09-12 09:47:46', '<b>  schurikvs</b>\n\n<b>  </b>September 2016\n\nwhat must I do to make it all it is thus in the front area on German\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\n<b>  </b>September 2016\n\nYou can use any localization plugin like Loco Translate or any other you know and are familiar with.\n\nOr you can use any Software to generate .po and .mo files and place is under langague folder in our plugin.', 'Plugin Usage', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '202-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-12 09:47:46', '2016-09-12 09:47:46', '', 202, 'http://127.0.0.1/202-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(916, 1, '2016-09-12 10:03:27', '2016-09-12 10:03:27', '<b>TheChrisLusk</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nNot getting emails of new tickets now. All of sudden we just stopped receiving them.\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nCan you please once get in touch with your host provider and have them look into the STMP server for any blocks or anything. Also ask them to check the email logs and see if they can find anything important for us to debug the issue.\n\n<b>TheChrisLusk</b>\n\nAugust 2016\n\nIts weird, its been spotty. Sometimes we get them now and sometimes we don’t. I will keep an eye on it.', 'Email Errors', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '204-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-12 10:03:27', '2016-09-12 10:03:27', '', 204, 'http://127.0.0.1/204-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(917, 1, '2016-09-12 10:04:42', '2016-09-12 10:04:42', '<b>webks</b>\n\n<b> </b>September 2016\n<ol>\n 	<li>I have the ability to add your own translation? 2. The source code is open to change?</li>\n</ol>\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\n<b> </b>September 2016\n<ol>\n 	<li>Yes, you can translate the plugin into any language. 2. The code is open. Once you are free to modify it as you may but the modification done by a third party will be out of scope in reagards to techncial support.</li>\n</ol>\n<b>webks</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n<ol>\n 	<li>Whether the user can change their password?</li>\n 	<li>Can I add additional files to the ticket, microsoft word?</li>\n 	<li>Is it possible to increase the size of uploaded files?</li>\n 	<li>Is there any custom requirements of hosting a script?</li>\n 	<li>Is the script has an account administrator? It can create an account users?</li>\n 	<li>The script can be only one department that answers your questions?</li>\n</ol>\n<b>webks</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\n?\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\n<b> </b>September 2016\n<ol>\n 	<li>The user can change their password. As user management is not maintained by our plugin. Our plugin uses the user’s registered via normal WordPress register page or any other registration plugin you might be using.</li>\n 	<li>Yes, you can add additional fields to Submit New Ticket form.</li>\n 	<li>Yes, the upload size depends upon the size allocated to your WordPress.</li>\n 	<li>No custom requirements as such, just your server should support AngularJS and the JS and CSS scripts included on the support page should not be minified like by CloudFlare or any other similar service.</li>\n 	<li>The WordPress admin is the admin of the tickets as well. He as full right over it and also create a ticket on the behalf of a customer or client.</li>\n 	<li>Yes, you can create or choose only department who can answer the tickets.</li>\n</ol>\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>webks</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nCool thanks.', 'Adding Translation', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '206-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-12 10:04:42', '2016-09-12 10:04:42', '', 206, 'http://127.0.0.1/206-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(918, 1, '2016-09-12 10:08:38', '2016-09-12 10:08:38', '<b>sarah23</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nVery nice and useful plugin. I am curious whether i can create more product along with Envato Item Sync.\n\nAdded Envato items but not able to create other custom product. Plz guide me.\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nYou can create new products by going to Tickets and under Tickets section you would find Products.\n\nIt’s just like you add a category to a post.', 'Entavo Item Sync', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '210-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-12 10:08:38', '2016-09-12 10:08:38', '', 210, 'http://127.0.0.1/210-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(919, 1, '2016-09-12 10:10:34', '2016-09-12 10:10:34', '<b>theme-plus</b>\n\nSeptember 2016\n\nI’m want to integrate your plugin and WooCommerce plugin. Project is about selling Services.\n\nProject Requirement is :\n<ol>\n 	<li>Users select the services and place the order. (WooCommerce)</li>\n 	<li>After placing order, thanks page will re-direct to automatically created support ticket. Using their order input details.</li>\n 	<li>Created ticket should be private mode for that specific user(client) and our wordpress admin role(support agent).</li>\n</ol>\nI just want :\n<ol>\n 	<li>Creating private ticket using your plugin API. Just putting ticket title and content.</li>\n 	<li>Ticket created user and our WordPress admin users will see and access the ticket. All other public users and other logged users will not see this ticket.</li>\n</ol>\nI want to use your plugin as messaging system between me and my customers.\n\nPlease let me know, is possible with your plugin and how?\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nOctober 2016\n\nAuto creation of ticket after an order from WooCommerce is not possible. Auto creation happens only from IMAP, where email received from the given email address under IMAP Configuration is converted into a ticket.\n\nAll the tickets are for private viewing between the admin, agent and the person who has created the ticket. Unless you specifically make the ticket as public.', 'Woocommerce Plugin', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '212-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-12 10:10:34', '2016-09-12 10:10:34', '', 212, 'http://127.0.0.1/212-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(920, 1, '2016-09-14 04:39:23', '2016-09-14 04:39:23', '<b>frymde</b>\n\nAugust 2016\n\nI have a new question. If a client already send an email with a subject “One”. When a client send a new email with a suject “Two”, this email is generate as ticket update from subject One or in a new ticket? How is it possible that all history from the same client could be find in only one big ticket?\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nAugust 2016\n\nIt would create a different ticket each time with different subject or email.\n\nIt is not possible to create a one big ticket unless all the conversation happens under one ticket itself. I mean we cannot group multiple tickets into one ticket.\n\n<b> frymde</b>\n\nAugust 2016\n\nOk. Thanks.\n\n&nbsp;', 'Ticket Enquiry', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '239-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-09-14 04:39:23', '2016-09-14 04:39:23', '', 239, 'http://127.0.0.1/239-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(921, 1, '2016-08-14 05:52:30', '2016-08-14 05:52:30', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>sphynxma</strong></p>\nAugust 2016\n\n</div>\nI tried logging into the support site to check for your response to my last inquiry. The site appears to be down. Are you no longer supporting this plugin?\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>CSSJockey</strong></p>\nAugust 2016\n\nSorry for the trouble. We’ve fixed our support site.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>', 'Plugin Error', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '260-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-14 05:52:30', '2016-08-14 05:52:30', '', 260, 'http://127.0.0.1/260-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(922, 1, '2016-08-14 05:58:02', '2016-08-14 05:58:02', '<strong>KPR</strong>\n\nAugust 2016\n\nViewing the demo site on an iPad, causes the top menubar to be 2 lines.. is there a fix for this?? I can post a picture somewhere if you like..\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>KPR</strong></p>\nAugust 2016\n\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted"><a href="http://prnt.sc/ccymqx" rel="nofollow">http://prnt.sc/ccymqx</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_14149237" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><strong>cjrupak</strong></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n\nAugust 2016\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nThis can be resolved with few CSS tweaks. Are you in iPad Mini or iPad2?\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_14149319" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>KPR</strong></p>\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0">August 2016</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">iPad 2..</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n<strong>cjrupak</strong>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_14149350" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div>August 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nAlright, we will give it a test drive here too on iPad2 and get back to you with the results.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Demo Site Error', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '262-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-14 05:58:02', '2016-08-14 05:58:02', '', 262, 'http://127.0.0.1/262-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(923, 1, '2016-08-14 06:14:02', '2016-08-14 06:14:02', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>plabanm</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">August 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHow does it work with woocommerce ? please tell me in details as I am building a e-commerce main interest is that.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"><strong>cjrupak </strong></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_14187203" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">August 2016</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\n&nbsp;\n\nFor woocommerce you can only export/sync the WooCommere products as plugin’s products, so that the user can choose the product they are seeking or support help for.\n\nThat’s all there is for WooCommerce.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Woocommerce Details', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '264-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-14 06:14:02', '2016-08-14 06:14:02', '', 264, 'http://127.0.0.1/264-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(924, 1, '2016-08-14 06:16:37', '2016-08-14 06:16:37', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>Harlock_ </strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">August 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nHi, is there a link for every single SCR I can give to visitors for specific support about topics? Thanks, Francesco\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-inject-target comment__action-container is-hidden"></div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_14149153" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><strong>cjrupak</strong></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n\nAugust 2016\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nYes, you can give link for every SCR, just take a look at SCR in WP Dashboard.\n\nIt is basically a custom post type with a permalink of it’s own like any other post or page.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_14149168" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><strong>Harlock_  </strong></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">August 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nOk, now I’ve noticed them. Thanks. Have a nice day, Francesco\n<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>cjrupak </strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">August 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nYou are welcome!\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Link For SCR', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '267-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-14 06:16:37', '2016-08-14 06:16:37', '', 267, 'http://127.0.0.1/267-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(925, 1, '2016-08-14 06:36:10', '2016-08-14 06:36:10', '<div class="media__body -align-center -basis-30">\n<p class="t-body -weight-bold h-m0"><strong>maioona</strong></p>\n\n</div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">August 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">if i dont have products i can remove this section? what about departments?</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\ncan i custm feilds?\n\nif a support agent is logged in, can he make a ticket on behalf of users? i dont see drop down menu, i must KNOW the name and spelling, is there a soultion for this?\n\nwhere can i see admin demo? in wordpress admin please\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="js-comment comment__item-response">\n<div id="comment_14187065" class="comment__info">\n<div class="media">\n<div class="media__item"><strong>cjrupak</strong></div>\n<div class="media__body -align-center">\n<div class="js-comment-tools comment__meta">August 2016</div>\n<div></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class="comment__body--response">\n<div class="js-comment__body t-preformatted">\n\nYou cannot remove products or departments as those are mandatory for the plugin to work but certainly you can hide them from the frontend via CSS.\n\nYes, a support agent can create a ticket on the behalf of a client.\n\nYou can check and use our plugin by creating a demo site at : <a href="http://cssjockey.net/" rel="nofollow">http://cssjockey.net/</a>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'Admin Demo', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '269-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-08-14 06:36:10', '2016-08-14 06:36:10', '', 269, 'http://127.0.0.1/269-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(926, 1, '2016-10-12 07:40:42', '2016-10-12 07:40:42', '<b>JoseDone</b>\n\nOctober 2016\n\nI want to know if the plugin support RTL or not , cause I need to use it with arabic language\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nOctober 2016\n\nSorry but our plugin does not support RTL right now.\n\n&nbsp;', 'Plugin Support RTL', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '144-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-12 07:40:42', '2016-10-12 07:40:42', '', 144, 'http://127.0.0.1/144-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(927, 1, '2016-10-12 07:42:32', '2016-10-12 07:42:32', '<b>InvidiaMarketing</b>\n\nOctober 2016\n\nis possible to change layout with my website? I want to include ticket system into my theme and not in new layout.\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nNovember 2016\n\nYou can run the support app with a page by adding a shortcode to any page or post with Theme’s header and footer.\n\nPlease follow this link for more info : <a href="http://docs.cssjockey.com/cjsupport/run-app-within-a-page-with-header-and-footer/">http://docs.cssjockey.com/cjsupport/run-app-within-a-page-with-header-and-footer/</a>', 'Change Layout with Website', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '146-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-10-12 07:42:32', '2016-10-12 07:42:32', '', 146, 'http://127.0.0.1/146-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(928, 1, '2016-11-12 07:44:01', '2016-11-12 07:44:01', '<b>Bioethics</b>\n\nNovember 2016\n\nHow long is the PO file for translation? (I only have a limited number of staff, so if the PO file is too long, maybe this plugin is not for us.)', 'PO File for Translation', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '148-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-11-12 07:44:01', '2016-11-12 07:44:01', '', 148, 'http://127.0.0.1/148-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(929, 1, '2016-11-12 07:45:40', '2016-11-12 07:45:40', '<b>Bioethics </b>\n\n<b> </b>November 2016\n\nIs your demo system broken? I’ve created demo at<a href="http://cssjockey.net/demo/gyy3ywx0a8"> http://cssjockey.net/demo/gyy3ywx0a8</a> , but it doesn’t work.', 'Demo System Broken', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '151-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-11-12 07:45:40', '2016-11-12 07:45:40', '', 151, 'http://127.0.0.1/151-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(930, 1, '2016-11-12 07:48:00', '2016-11-12 07:48:00', '<b>milo75</b>\n\nNovember 2016\n\nGreat job on the support system chaps. One suggestion; When you log in, instead of having a blank page maybe it can redirect you to your open tickets. Saves a click and it looks better than just a blank page.\n\n<b>milo75</b>\n\n<b> </b>November 2016\n\nAlso having the option to disable certain email notifications would be nice. Same as the auto close notification where you have the option to disable it. Can we have this for all notifications please so we can turn it on or off.\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nNovember 2016\n\nFine suggestions, we will try and include this in the upcoming version of the plugin.\n\nYou can also join us on our Facebook group to suggest any other feature (s) you wish to see in any of our product : <a href="https://facebook.com/groups/cssjockey.ib">https://facebook.com/groups/cssjockey.ib</a>', 'Disable Auto Notification', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '153-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-11-12 07:48:00', '2016-11-12 07:48:00', '', 153, 'http://127.0.0.1/153-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(931, 1, '2016-11-12 07:52:19', '2016-11-12 07:52:19', '<b>galaxy5</b>\n\nNovember 2016\n\nPrepurchase question: With email piping can we use our own custom SMTP like mailgun instead of our the server, I don’t want our original IP address leaking out.\n\n<b>CSSJockey</b>\n\n<b> </b>November 2016\n\nthe current version uses only php imap for email piping. However, we will consider adding more services in our upcoming version.', 'Email Piping', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '155-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-11-12 07:52:19', '2016-11-12 07:52:19', '', 155, 'http://127.0.0.1/155-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(932, 1, '2016-11-12 07:56:21', '2016-11-12 07:56:21', '<b>Bioethics</b>\n\nNovember 2016\n\nIt won’t install. It triggers “The package could not be installed. No valid plugins were found. Plugin install failed.” error. What gives?\n\n<b>Bioethics</b>\n\nNovember 2016\n\nfigured that one out on my own. I was supposed to extract the zip file inside the downloaded zip. newbie mistake.', 'Plugin Error', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '157-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-11-12 07:56:21', '2016-11-12 07:56:21', '', 157, 'http://127.0.0.1/157-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(933, 1, '2016-11-12 07:58:20', '2016-11-12 07:58:20', '<b>webks</b>\n\n<b> </b>November 2016\n\nHello, please tell to the ticket: BIGYU5K58A3256 From 4 days 0 contact.\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nNovember 2016\n\nIt has been replied.', 'Tell to the Ticket', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '159-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-11-12 07:58:20', '2016-11-12 07:58:20', '', 159, 'http://127.0.0.1/159-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(934, 1, '2016-11-12 08:00:21', '2016-11-12 08:00:21', '<b>m2farma</b>\n\nNovember 2016\n\nHello, could you tell us when will next version be avaiable?\n\n<b>CSSJockey</b>\n\nNovember 2016\n\nHi, its taking time, will try to release the new version this month.', 'Next Version', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '161-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-11-12 08:00:21', '2016-11-12 08:00:21', '', 161, 'http://127.0.0.1/161-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(935, 1, '2016-11-12 08:01:59', '2016-11-12 08:01:59', '<b>nouredin</b>\n\n<b> </b>November 2016\n\nI’m wondering if I can create a new ticket in php code and fill it with specific data.\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nNovember 2016\n\nCan you give us a example on how you are planning to do that.\n\n` This app is based on AngularJS and uses WordPress as a medium to manage content.\n\nThe Tickets are custom post type and the replies to the tickets are the commnens on that post type.\n\nHope this info helps a little.\n\n<b>nouredin</b>\n\nNovember 2016\n\nI need to create a ticket automatically when a user registers a new account containing his/her name and some information.\n\nIt would be great if you have an API or similar stuff to do that.\n\n<b>nouredin</b>\n\n<b> </b>November 2016\n\nI can use a WP function to create the custom post type and it’s custom fields, but this won’t trigger other functions I guess (sending an email for example).\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nNovember 2016\n\nWe don’t have a public API as of now but we are working on it.\n\nYes, it won’t trigger other functions from within the app.', 'New Ticket in php Code', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '163-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-11-12 08:01:59', '2016-11-12 08:01:59', '', 163, 'http://127.0.0.1/163-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(936, 1, '2016-11-12 08:10:54', '2016-11-12 08:10:54', '<b>DJNume</b>\n\nNovember 2016\n\n&nbsp;\n\nIs it possible to have conditional questions for the form. Lets say the person picks option A for the support, I want it to display Question #1. If he picks B for support, Question #2 is displayed instead.\n\nAlso, is there a front-end admin page – so I don’t have to give support ticket agents access to the admin panel?\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nNovember 2016\n\n&nbsp;\n<ol>\n 	<li>Conditional dropdowns are not available in this version.</li>\n 	<li>Agents does not need to access the admin area to manage tickets, they can manage everything related to a ticket via front-end like replying, uploading and downloading files, etc..</li>\n</ol>\nThe only case i think we would need to access the admin area if they want to change something in their profile as user management like login and registration, etc.. is not managed by our plugin.', 'Ticket Agent Access', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '166-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-11-12 08:10:54', '2016-11-12 08:10:54', '', 166, 'http://127.0.0.1/166-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0) ;
