(1016, 1, '2017-03-12 06:18:16', '2017-03-12 06:18:16', '<b>Awiwichannel</b>\n\n<b>    </b>March 2017\n\n&nbsp;\n\nHello, wonder if this ticket system will do what i have in mind, what im looking for is a way to sell blundle tickets lets say of 10 20 or 30 support tickets with woocommerce, if a person buys the first one with 10 tickets and use a ticket and everything gets solved, a ticked will be removed so there will be 9 tickets left to use. Is this possible with your plugin? it has nice reviews and i hope it works i cant find anything to do what i have in mind.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>cjrupak</b>\n\nMarch 2017\n\n&nbsp;\n\nSorry, but we do not have such a feature in this plugin as of now.\n\nAll the best for your continued search and I hope you find a plugin that meets your requirement.\n\n&nbsp;', 'Support Tickets with woocommerce', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'support-tickets-with-woocommerce', '', '', '2017-03-12 06:18:16', '2017-03-12 06:18:16', '', 0, 'http://gnosia.pauple.com/?post_type=pauple_helpie&amp;p=74', 0, 'pauple_helpie', '', 0),
